VALUES ('I Would Buy In 2025, But‚Ä¶', 'i-would-buy-in-2025-but', '<p id="">Buying a home in 2025 might be on a lot of people‚Äôs minds‚Äîbut what‚Äôs holding them back? Price? Timing? Selling first? You won‚Äôt know unless you ask.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">That‚Äôs what this poll is built for. It‚Äôs an easy, low-commitment way for buyers to tell you what‚Äôs really standing in their way‚Äîwithout feeling pressured. Every response gives you a reason to reach out, start a conversation, and position yourself as the agent who understands their situation.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Use this poll to spark engagement, uncover hesitation, and find your next client.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/i-would-buy-in-2025-but/thumbnail-i-would-buy-in-2025-but.png', false, 'static_image', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGfwzdIezs/B_-vrZiSZYjOJ_1_cuZiSg/view?utm_content=DAGfwzdIezs&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b3c5fd1ff8bd0fdc5ee861/67c0d2570fef90b7c265260f_4Main%20Image%20To%20upload--421412-2.png', NULL, '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Post to Instagram","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Start a New Story: Open Instagram and create a new story.</li><li id=\"\">Add Poll Sticker: Tap the <strong id=\"\">Sticker icon</strong> and select <strong id=\"\">Poll.</strong></li><li id=\"\">Set Up Poll:</li></ol><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Set answer options <br><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Option 1: <strong id=\"\">\"Too expensive\"</strong></li><li id=\"\">Option 2: <strong id=\"\">\"Nothing I love\"</strong></li><li id=\"\">Option 3: \"<strong id=\"\">Need to sell first</strong>\"</li><li id=\"\">Option 4: \"<strong id=\"\">I do want to buy!</strong>\"</li></ul></li></ul><ol start=\"4\" id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Position Poll: Place the poll in the designated spot on the image.</li><li id=\"\">Share: Tap \"Your Story\" to publish.</li></ol><p id=\"\">‚Äç<em id=\"\">See the image below to view how the post appears to your audience.</em></p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

