VALUES ('21 Headline PDF', '21-headline-pdf', '<p id="">Smart agents are investing their resources into generating seller leads through paid social and display advertising&nbsp;</p><p id="">But as advertising dollars flood the feed, we‚Äôre going to see a rise in the traditional ads like this:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><figure class="w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-center" data-rt-type="image" data-rt-align="center"><div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/65b3c5fd1ff8bd0fdc5ee861/6644d24c1566a683ea2ad377_We0Juy2OahejPaA6m7qWUzVkKCMoUaHVSuYORn-CrsCrrCovm9a_Nn_kc5xbwhqoAG_j9dkK80HZAO9Mof97FSRN8P25YKGe1hVXwptUZJKNanlKc7f-5RRlGvXHz8NHd6oEYLOPj_Kb1JKn4mJvZC0.jpeg" width="auto" height="auto" alt="" loading="auto" id=""></div></figure><p id=""><br>When it comes to advertising, you can‚Äôt bore people into clicking.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you want to increase your performance, you have to create unique ad campaigns that are unlike your competitors.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">That‚Äôs why we put together a list of 21 Irresistible Seller Hooks that you can use in your ads, emails, postcards and websites. <br><br></p><p id="">Let‚Äôs get to work! </p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/21-headline-pdf/thumbnail-21-headline-pdf.png', false, 'static_image', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/12UDuASQlV6TSASuWotefTa8iFxCE-zR5/view?usp=sharing', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/21-headline-pdf/example-21-headline-pdf.png'], '[{"title":"Download PDF","body":""}]', 'US', false, true);

