VALUES ('A Lot Of Clients Are Cashing Out Their Equity', 'client-equity', '<p id="">Inspired by <a href="https://www.instagram.com/kenpozek/" target="_blank">Ken Pozek‚Äôs</a> Instagram Story, this is a perfect campaign to use when you want to convert through Instagram Stories‚Äîwhether you have a Just Sold listing to promote or not.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">The reason why this campaign is so effective is that it leans into the ‚Äúherd mentality‚Äù‚Äîthe idea that consumers tend to follow the actions and choices of a larger group, often driven by social proof and the perception that popular decisions are the safest or best.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">If you‚Äôve recently sold a home, use this campaign to showcase your listing. And if you haven‚Äôt recently sold a home, use it as an opportunity to showcase homes that have sold recently in a specific neighborhood for the same effect.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/client-equity/thumbnail-client-equity.png', false, 'static_image', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGfFYoNslg/SktjWCC9VnRItiZjn_pfng/view?utm_content=DAGfFYoNslg&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/client-equity/example-client-equity.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Post to Instagram","body":"<p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">1. Start a New Post:</strong> Open Instagram and tap the <strong id=\"\">+</strong> icon to create a new post.</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">2. Select Carousel Format:</strong> Tap <strong id=\"\">Select Multiple</strong> (icon with stacked squares) to enable carousel posting.</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">3. Choose Your Images/Videos:</strong></p><ul id=\"\"><li>Select up to 10 images or videos for your carousel.</li></ul><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">4. Arrange Your Slides:</strong></p><ul id=\"\"><li>Drag and reorder the selected files to your preferred order.</li></ul><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">6. Write a Caption:</strong> Add a compelling caption to accompany your carousel.</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">7. Add Tags &amp; Location (Optional):</strong></p><ul id=\"\"><li>Tag people, add hashtags, and include a location if relevant.</li></ul><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">8. Share Your Post:</strong> Tap <strong id=\"\">Share</strong> to publish your carousel.</p><p id=\"\"><em id=\"\">See the image below to view how the carousel appears on your profile.</em></p><p id=\"\">‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

