VALUES ('Client Success Story: Worried about fixing up your home before you sell?', 'worried-about-fixing-up-your-home-before-you-sell-client-success-story', '<p id="">Most sellers assume they need to spend <em id="">thousands</em> fixing up their home before listing. But what if that‚Äôs not actually the case?</p><p id="">This Instagram carousel doesn‚Äôt just challenge that assumption‚Äîit proves it wrong with a real success story. Instead of pushing renovations, it walks homeowners through a <em id="">real-life example</em> of a seller who skipped the costly upgrades, found the right buyer, and walked away with $XX,XXX more than they would have made with an iBuyer.</p><p id="">By the end, the message is clear: before they spend a dime, they should DM you first. Real results, real strategy, and a CTA designed to start conversations. Let‚Äôs get it posted!</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/worried-about-fixing-up-your-home-before-you-sell-client-success-story/thumbnail-worried-about-fixing-up-your-home-before-you-sell-client-success-story.png', false, 'static_image', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGebUFDlIk/Pfn7r9gBAZ5-8Ll7HAnrBw/view?utm_content=DAGebUFDlIk&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/worried-about-fixing-up-your-home-before-you-sell-client-success-story/example-worried-about-fixing-up-your-home-before-you-sell-client-success-story.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Post to Instagram","body":"<p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">1. Start a New Post:</strong> Open Instagram and tap the <strong id=\"\">+</strong> icon to create a new post.</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">2. Select Carousel Format:</strong> Tap <strong id=\"\">Select Multiple</strong> (icon with stacked squares) to enable carousel posting.</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">3. Choose Your Images/Videos:</strong></p><ul id=\"\"><li>Select up to 10 images or videos for your carousel.</li></ul><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">4. Arrange Your Slides:</strong></p><ul id=\"\"><li>Drag and reorder the selected files to your preferred order.</li></ul><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">6. Write a Caption:</strong> Add a compelling caption to accompany your carousel.</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">7. Add Tags &amp; Location (Optional):</strong></p><ul id=\"\"><li>Tag people, add hashtags, and include a location if relevant.</li></ul><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">8. Share Your Post:</strong> Tap <strong id=\"\">Share</strong> to publish your carousel.</p><p id=\"\"><em id=\"\">See the image below to view how the carousel appears on your profile.</em></p><p id=\"\">‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

