VALUES ('Have you received your 2024 Home Value Report from your agent yet?', 'have-you-received-your-2024-home-value-report-from-your-agent-yet', '<p id="">This campaign is designed to trigger the consumers fear of missing out.&nbsp;</p><p id="">By implying they <em id="">should</em> have received this report, it can elicit an emotion that they are missing out on important information.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Which then ‚Äì creates an opportunity for you to connect, engage and build a new relationship with an abandoned seller.&nbsp;</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/have-you-received-your-2024-home-value-report-from-your-agent-yet/thumbnail-have-you-received-your-2024-home-value-report-from-your-agent-yet.png', false, 'static_image', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGZeFMHhSI/Z5qm8Y8J7xZrvYHWm_GJxw/view?utm_content=DAGZeFMHhSI&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/have-you-received-your-2024-home-value-report-from-your-agent-yet/example-have-you-received-your-2024-home-value-report-from-your-agent-yet.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Post to Instagram","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Start a New Story: Open Instagram and create a new story.</li><li>Add Poll Sticker: Tap the <strong id=\"\">Sticker icon</strong> and select <strong id=\"\">Poll.</strong></li><li>Set Up Poll:</li></ol><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Set answer optionssome text<ul id=\"\"><li>Option 1: <strong id=\"\">\"Nope!\"</strong></li><li>Option 2: <strong id=\"\">\"What‚Äôs included in the report?\"</strong>‚Äç</li><li>Option 3:&nbsp;<strong id=\"\">\"I want one for my home!&nbsp;\"</strong></li></ul></li></ul><ol start=\"4\" id=\"\"><li>Position Poll: Place the poll in the designated spot on the image.</li><li>Share: Tap \"Your Story\" to publish.</li></ol><p id=\"\">‚Äç<em id=\"\">See the image below to view how the post appears to your audience.</em></p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

