VALUES ('Home Value IG Video', 'home-value-ig-video', '<p id="">The typical home value ad is overused.</p><p id="">Over-advertised.</p><p id="">So let''s try something different‚Ä¶</p><p id="">Most agents don‚Äôt know that you can generate seller leads with Instagram Stories.&nbsp;</p><p id="">But there‚Äôs a catch‚Ä¶</p><p id="">If you‚Äôre going to be posting stories on Instagram, you need to be using polls and questions.&nbsp;</p><p id="">These are simple interactive tools that turn impressions into warm leads.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Here''s an Instagram story template you can use to generate "inbound" IG leads.</p><p id="">All you have to do is add the poll (with no title).</p><p id="">Then add these poll answers:</p><p id=""><em id="">In the last 7 days.</em></p><p id=""><em id="">It''s been a while.</em></p><p id=""><em id="">It''s been way too long.</em></p><p id="">When people respond to the poll, slide into their DMs with the following scripts:</p><p id=""><em id="">In the last 7 days</em> ‚Üí What do you think about the value?</p><p id=""><em id="">It''s been a while</em> or <em id="">way too long</em> ‚Üí Would it be helpful if I prepared a professional home value report for you?</p><p id="">IG stories are a cheat code for seller leads.</p><p id="">You can post this today. ‚¨áÔ∏è</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/home-value-ig-video/thumbnail-home-value-ig-video.png', false, 'static_image', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ahpNHtPLettdmqcOZ2oXIYSJypLlqlBa/view?fbclid=IwAR2HR-DZ2DS4i_HONkvp3cHQodRRqBB_NHj-dNiaVsaFfGQ6GqimF82z5xw_aem_ATCwJw22F2C2YeWA_SQC0ZHFLZcjgcWsCFZnX78N8Fhb_KhuDP5KIjaqo1jQfdOcRkpqiCajwLR8FTymlECpbEn_', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/home-value-ig-video/example-home-value-ig-video.gif'], '[{"title":"Download the Video","body":""},{"title":"Add Instagram poll","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Start a New Story: Open Instagram and create a new story.</li><li>Add Poll Sticker: Tap the <strong id=\"\">Sticker icon</strong> and select <strong id=\"\">Poll.</strong></li><li>Set Up Poll:</li></ol><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Set answer options <br><ul id=\"\"><li>Option 1: <strong id=\"\">\"A while ago‚Ä¶\"</strong></li><li>Option 2: <strong id=\"\">\"It''s been years!\"</strong></li><li>Option 3: <strong>\"Never‚Ä¶ maybe I should!\"</strong></li></ul></li></ul><ol start=\"4\" id=\"\"><li>Position Poll: Place the poll in the designated spot on the image.</li><li>Share: Tap \"Your Story\" to publish.</li></ol><p id=\"\">‚Äç<em id=\"\">See the image below to view how the post appears to your audience.</em></p><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

