VALUES ('I''m about to go meet a potential seller IG Story', 'im-about-to-go-meet-a-potential-seller-ig-story', '<p id="">This is rarely talked about in the real estate marketing world but one of the best ways to attract high-quality seller leads is by doing high-quality marketing of your current listings.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Prior to the home going on the market, post this to your Instagram Story to build the buzz and interest.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It''s a simple way to add incredible value to both potential buyers and your seller. ‚¨áÔ∏è</p>', NULL, false, 'static_image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'US', false, true);

