VALUES ('Just Sold Zestimate Post', 'just-sold-zestimate-post', '<p id="">Here''s how you can generate Instagram Seller Leads using the Zestimate. ‚¨áÔ∏è</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Step 1: Always take a photo of the Zestimate <em id="">before</em> you put it in the MLS. This helps you avoid Zillow''s fancy algorithm from&nbsp; taking credit for your pricing strategy.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Step 2: When you sell the home above the Zestimate, promote it as an IG story.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Step 3: Create a poll with the question: <em id="">Is your Zestimate accurate?</em></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Step 4: DM every person who responds to the poll with a CMA offer: <em id="">Hey [First Name], I noticed that you responded that our Zestimate was wrong. Would it be helpful if I put together a professional home equity for your home? It will be much more accurate than an online tool.</em></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Step 5: Schedule calls to review the results with your prospects.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">NOTABLY: If you don''t have a good example of a Zestimate, skip step 1 and 2 and go right to step 3.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/just-sold-zestimate-post/thumbnail-just-sold-zestimate-post.png', false, 'static_image', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAF_DD561BQ/JilCFfbvqyEcFhvTR5Actw/view?utm_content=DAF_DD561BQ&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/just-sold-zestimate-post/example-just-sold-zestimate-post.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Post to Instagram","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Start a New Story: Open Instagram and create a new story.</li><li id=\"\">Add Poll Sticker: Tap the <strong id=\"\">Sticker icon</strong> and select <strong id=\"\">Poll.</strong></li><li id=\"\">Set Up Poll:</li></ol><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Set answer options<ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Option 1: <strong id=\"\">\"Yes, it''s Right.\"</strong></li><li id=\"\">Option 2: \"<strong id=\"\">It''s wrong</strong>\"</li><li id=\"\">Option 3: <strong id=\"\">\"I don''t know\"</strong></li></ul></li></ul><ol start=\"4\" id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Position Poll: Place the poll in the designated spot on the image.</li><li id=\"\">Share: Tap \"Your Story\" to publish.</li></ol><p id=\"\">‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

