VALUES ('Look Up Your First Home On Zillow', 'look-up-your-first-home-on-zillow', '<p id="">This is a üî• social media tactic.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Leverage IG polls or a Facebook post to ask an engaging question, then DM people who respond.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">This is a rinse and repeat strategy that you can leverage each week to have more real estate related conversations with people who are connected with you on social media.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Watch the magic unfold when you stop scrolling and start engaging.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/look-up-your-first-home-on-zillow/thumbnail-look-up-your-first-home-on-zillow.png', false, 'static_image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/look-up-your-first-home-on-zillow/example-1-look-up-your-first-home-on-zillow.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/look-up-your-first-home-on-zillow/example-2-look-up-your-first-home-on-zillow.png'], '[{"title":"Choose right photo for your story","body":""},{"title":"Add Question","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Start a New Story: Open Instagram and create a new story.</li><li id=\"\">Add Question Sticker: Tap the <strong id=\"\">Sticker icon</strong> and select <strong id=\"\">Question</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Set Up Question: <br><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Type your question prompt: <strong id=\"\">Look up your first home on Zillow and tell me what you paid and what it''s Zillow Zestimate is now.... </strong></li></ul></li><li id=\"\">Position Question: Place the question sticker in the designated spot on the image.</li><li id=\"\">Share: Tap \"Your Story\" to publish.</li></ol><p id=\"\"><em id=\"\">See the image below to view how the post appears to your audience.</em></p><p id=\"\">‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

