VALUES ('Magic Buyer Video', 'magic-buyer-video', '<p id="">If you have a qualified buyer, but nowhere for them to go, that''s not a problem‚Äîit''s an opportunity.<br>‚Äç<br>That''s exactly what the 2024 Magic Buyer Video is about.<br>‚Äç<br>It''s an opportunity for you to go the extra mile for your buyer.<br>‚Äç<br>It''s an opportunity for you to start more conversations.<br>‚Äç<br>It''s an opportunity for you to generate more listing opportunities.<br>‚Äç<br>As you adapt this campaign to fit your market, your buyer, and your brand, make sure you include:<br>‚Äç<br>1. Specific data points about who your buyer is and what they''re looking for<br>2. Social proof to prove that you''re great at your job<br>3. Your personal cell number<br>4. A direct response CTA in the p.s</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/magic-buyer-video/thumbnail-magic-buyer-video.png', false, 'static_image', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dKZxRj51-TM', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'US', false, true);

