VALUES ('POV: Downsizing', 'pov-downsizing', '<p id="">POV hooks are effective because they tap into real, relatable experiences. That‚Äôs exactly what this campaign does: <em id="">POV: Downsizing</em> gives you the chance to connect with homeowners who might be quietly wrestling with the decision to downsize.</p><p id="">Plus it‚Äôs incredibly simple to execute. No script, no voiceover‚Äîjust b-roll from your camera roll (a neighborhood <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFJFzauzFmX/" id="">like in this example</a>, a listing interior <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEVxvHlSFjQ/" id="">like in this example</a>, even a front door <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C-cBP43u73z/" id="">like in this example</a>). Overlay with text, and let the caption do the heavy lifting. It doesn‚Äôt need to be super polished, the priority here is a clear message.</p><p id="">This campaign isn‚Äôt just a Reel. It‚Äôs a chance to build trust, share your expertise, and position yourself as the agent who goes beyond what‚Äôs expected. Keep it real, keep it relatable‚Äîand make sure to end with a call to action that invites them to engage, like commenting <em id="">GUIDE</em> to take the next step.</p><p id="">Use the Video Description below as your Instagram Reel caption.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/pov-downsizing/thumbnail-pov-downsizing.png', true, 'video', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGdIhqclI0/hY143O-ZR78n7l336w45Hw/view?utm_content=DAGdIhqclI0&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', 'Show Flow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Deciding to downsize isn‚Äôt easy‚Äîit‚Äôs emotional, and it takes time to know if it‚Äôs the right move.¬†But when it is‚Ä¶a fresh start can be life-changing. Here are 5 signs it might be time to downsize: 1. Your monthly costs feel unnecessarily high. 2. You have rooms that sit empty, except for storage. 3. Your utility bills keep skyrocketing. 4. You‚Äôre craving more freedom to travel on your own terms. 5. The upkeep on your home feels like a constant burden.If this is something you‚Äôre considering (even just thinking about), comment GUIDE below to get my free downsizing guide & more info to help you make an informed decision. üëá', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/pov-downsizing/example-pov-downsizing.png'], '[{"title":"Record the Video","body":""},{"title":"Create Your Thumbnail","body":""}]', 'US', false, true);

