VALUES ('POV: You Finally Find A Home You Love...', 'pov-off-market-2', '<p id="">POV hooks are powerful‚Äîand for good reason. They pull your audience in by speaking directly to their experience. That‚Äôs exactly what this campaign does: it gives you a chance to educate your followers about your off-market strategy while showing them how you uncover hidden opportunities.</p><p id="">Plus it‚Äôs incredibly simple to execute. No script, no voiceover‚Äîjust b-roll from your camera roll (a neighborhood <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFJFzauzFmX/">like in this example</a>, a listing interior <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEVxvHlSFjQ/" id="">like in this example</a>, even a front door <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C-cBP43u73z/" id="">like in this example</a>). Overlay with text, and let the caption do the heavy lifting. It doesn‚Äôt need to be super polished, the priority here is a clear message.</p><p id="">The source of this data point mentioned in the description is from <a href="https://www.resiclubanalytics.com/p/lot-home-sales-happening-offmarketjust-look-map" id="">BatchService</a> and surfaced by Lance Lambert, co-founder of ResiClub:<br>‚Äç<br><em id="">According to an analysis by BatchService, approximately 1.2 million U.S. home sales in 2024 were conducted off-market. Given that the National Association of Realtors reported about 5 million existing-home sales in 2024, this suggests that roughly 24% of home sales occurred off-market.</em></p><p id="">This campaign isn‚Äôt just a Reel. It‚Äôs a chance to build trust, share your expertise, and position yourself as the agent who goes beyond what‚Äôs expected. Keep it real, keep it relatable‚Äîand don‚Äôt forget to end with a call to action that gets them to raise their hand.</p><p id="">Use the Video Description below as your Instagram Reel caption.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/pov-off-market-2/thumbnail-pov-off-market-2.png', true, 'video', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGdIkupYz8/dDwPbDLO71fTHK3b9gIeHQ/view?utm_content=DAGdIkupYz8&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', 'Show Flow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Did you know nearly 1 in 4 homes are sold off-market? That means your dream home‚Äîthe one that fits your budget and checks all your boxes‚Äîmight be out there, just not online. Here‚Äôs how we help clients find ‚Äúthe one,‚Äù even when it feels like there‚Äôs nothing out there‚Äî ‚úîÔ∏è We start by learning exactly what you‚Äôre looking for. ‚úîÔ∏è Then, we tap into our exclusive network of agents, builders, and homeowners open to an off-market deal. ‚úîÔ∏è Finally, we source an off-market property that feels like it was made for you. If you want access to off-market opportunities, comment VIP below. üëá', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/pov-off-market-2/example-pov-off-market-2.png'], '[{"title":"Record the Video","body":""},{"title":"Create Your Thumbnail","body":""}]', 'US', false, true);

