VALUES ('POV: You''re Tired of Scrolling Through Overpriced Homes', 'pov-off-market', '<p id="">POV hooks are powerful‚Äîand for good reason. They pull your audience in by speaking directly to their experience. That‚Äôs exactly what this campaign does: it gives you a chance to educate your followers about your off-market strategy while showing them how you uncover hidden opportunities.</p><p id="">Plus it‚Äôs incredibly simple to execute. No script, no voiceover‚Äîjust b-roll from your camera roll (a neighborhood <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFJFzauzFmX/">like in this example</a>, a listing interior <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEVxvHlSFjQ/" id="">like in this example</a>, even a front door <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C-cBP43u73z/" id="">like in this example</a>). Overlay with text, and let the caption do the heavy lifting. It doesn‚Äôt need to be super polished, the priority here is a clear message.</p><p id="">The source of this data point mentioned in the description is from <a href="https://www.resiclubanalytics.com/p/lot-home-sales-happening-offmarketjust-look-map" id="">BatchService</a> and surfaced by Lance Lambert, co-founder of ResiClub:<br>‚Äç<br><em id="">According to an analysis by BatchService, approximately 1.2 million U.S. home sales in 2024 were conducted off-market. Given that the National Association of Realtors reported about 5 million existing-home sales in 2024, this suggests that roughly 24% of home sales occurred off-market.</em></p><p id="">This campaign isn‚Äôt just a Reel. It‚Äôs a chance to build trust, share your expertise, and position yourself as the agent who goes beyond what‚Äôs expected. Keep it real, keep it relatable‚Äîand don‚Äôt forget to end with a call to action that gets them to raise their hand.</p><p id="">Use the Video Description below as your Instagram Reel caption.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/pov-off-market/thumbnail-pov-off-market.png', true, 'video', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGdIiSAcbU/yI9U8wAP7kfR3-_CnJEdoQ/view?utm_content=DAGdIiSAcbU&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', 'Show Flow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ever feel like the perfect home just doesn‚Äôt exist? (Or at least, not on Zillow?)¬†‚ÄçHere‚Äôs the thing most people don‚Äôt realize: about 24% of homes are sold off-market. That means the one you‚Äôre dreaming of‚Äîit might never make it online.‚Äç So, what do you do? You work with someone who knows how to find it.‚Äç I specialize in sourcing off-market properties through a strategic and highly connected approach. This includes tapping into our extensive network of agents, builders, and homeowners who‚Äôd be open to the possibility of an off-market deal.‚Äç It‚Äôs a game-changer for clients who‚Äôve been searching for months without luck.‚Äç So if you‚Äôre tired of scrolling through overpriced homes on Zillow‚Ä¶comment VIP to get insider access to off-market deals.', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/pov-off-market/example-pov-off-market.png'], '[{"title":"Record the Video","body":""},{"title":"Create Your Thumbnail","body":""}]', 'US', false, true);

