VALUES ('Social of the Week', 'social-of-the-week-4', '<p id="">Zillow‚Äôs report shows that the average homeowner spends 6-7 months considering selling before making a move.</p><p id="">That‚Äôs why it‚Äôs crucial for us to consistently stay in front of them‚Äîboth in their inbox and on their social feeds.</p><p id="">This campaign is crafted to demonstrate that we understand their journey and are ready to guide them every step of the way.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/social-of-the-week-4/thumbnail-social-of-the-week-4.png', false, 'static_image', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGS5jNmE-Y/H5XVZC-M1t2n1uMLsMXvMA/view?utm_content=DAGS5jNmE-Y&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qtBSoiWWHcc', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/social-of-the-week-4/example-social-of-the-week-4.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Post to Instagram","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Start a New Story: Open Instagram and create a new story.</li><li>Add Poll Sticker: Tap the <strong id=\"\">Sticker icon</strong> and select <strong id=\"\">Poll.</strong></li><li>Set Up Poll:</li></ol><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Set answer options <br><ul id=\"\"><li>Option 1: <strong id=\"\">\"I''m not moving until 2025\"</strong></li><li>Option 2: <strong id=\"\">\"I''m going to try to sell this year\"</strong></li><li>Option 3: \"<strong>I''m in my forever home</strong>\"</li></ul></li></ul><ol start=\"4\" id=\"\"><li>Position Poll: Place the poll in the designated spot on the image.</li><li>Share: Tap \"Your Story\" to publish.</li></ol><p id=\"\">‚Äç<em id=\"\">See the image below to view how the post appears to your audience.</em></p><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

