VALUES ('The Emotion-Driven Just Sold', 'the-emotion-driven-just-sold', '<p id="">Most ‚ÄúJust Sold‚Äù posts focus on the numbers‚Äîsale price, days on market, multiple offers. But this? This is about the <em id="">moment</em> a seller realizes their home is officially sold. The relief. The excitement. The deep breath after weeks (or months) of waiting.</p><p id="">Inspired by <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C146ftErfjH/" target="_blank">Bridgette Harrington‚Äôs viral reel</a>, this isn‚Äôt about data‚Äîit‚Äôs about the human side of real estate. The emotions, the milestones, the stories that make this job so rewarding.</p><p id="">This reel captures that moment. And trust me, it‚Äôs the kind of content people <em id="">feel</em>‚Äîwhich is exactly why it resonates.</p><h4 id=""><strong id="">How to Customize Your Instagram Reel Using Our Canva Template</strong></h4><p id="">We‚Äôve created a plug-and-play Canva template to help you easily produce a professional Instagram Reel.</p><h5 id=""><strong id="">Option 1: Use the Canva Template with Stock Photos or Videos</strong></h5><p id=""><strong>üîπ Step 1: </strong>Open the Canva template link provided. This will open the design in your Canva account. (If you don‚Äôt have an account, sign up for free at www.canva.com.)</p><p id=""><strong>üîπ Step 2: </strong>Click ‚ÄúUse Template‚Äù to create your own editable copy.</p><p id=""><strong>üîπ Step 3: </strong>Customize the text:</p><ul id=""><li id="">Double-click any text box to edit.</li><li id="">Adjust fonts and colors to match your branding (optional).</li></ul><p id="">üîπ Step 4: Add your logo (optional):</p><ul id=""><li id="">Upload your logo via ‚ÄúUploads‚Äù and drag it onto the template.</li></ul><p id="">üîπ<strong> Step 5:</strong> Download your video:</p><ul id=""><li id="">Click ‚ÄúShare‚Äù in the top right corner.</li><li id="">Select ‚ÄúDownload‚Äù &gt; Choose MP4 format &gt; Click Download.</li></ul><p id="">üîπ<strong> Step 6:</strong> Post to Instagram Reels:</p><ul id=""><li id="">Open Instagram and tap the + button, then select Reel.</li><li id="">Upload your customized video.</li><li id="">Add trending audio (optional), a compelling caption, and relevant hashtags.</li><li id="">Tap ‚ÄúShare‚Äù ‚Äî and you‚Äôre done!</li></ul><h5 id=""><strong id="">Option 2: Use Your Own Videos as the Background</strong></h5><p id="">Want to make your reel even more personal? Use photos or videos of your client''s property as the background while keeping the text animations and design from our template.</p><p id="">üîπ <strong>Step 1:</strong> Record or select a vertical video.</p><p id="">üîπ<strong> Step 2: </strong>Open the Canva template link and click ‚ÄúUse Template‚Äù to create your editable copy.</p><p id="">üîπ<strong> Step 3: </strong>Replace the background videos:</p><ul id=""><li id="">Click on the existing video in the template.</li><li id="">Choose ‚ÄúDelete‚Äù or ‚ÄúReplace background.‚Äù</li><li id="">Upload your video via ‚ÄúUploads‚Äù and drag it into the background frame.</li></ul><p id="">üîπ <strong>Step 4: </strong>Adjust the text &amp; design:</p><ul id=""><li id="">Ensure your text is still readable over your custom video.</li><li id="">Move or resize elements if needed.</li></ul><p id="">üîπ<strong> Step 5:</strong> Download your video:</p><ul id=""><li id="">Click ‚ÄúShare‚Äù in the top right corner.</li><li id="">Select ‚ÄúDownload‚Äù &gt; Choose MP4 format &gt; Click Download.</li></ul><p id="">üîπ <strong>Step 6: </strong>Post to Instagram Reels:</p><ul id=""><li id="">Open Instagram and tap the + button, then select Reel.</li><li id="">Upload your video.</li><li id="">Add trending audio (optional), a caption (which is included below), and relevant hashtags.</li><li id="">Tap ‚ÄúShare‚Äù ‚Äî and you‚Äôre done!</li></ul>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/the-emotion-driven-just-sold/thumbnail-the-emotion-driven-just-sold.png', true, 'video', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGhDqK0_cM/VJHCIDK2SlII-w3r9Dg7lg/view?utm_content=DAGhDqK0_cM&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When your client officially sells their home. üóù', ARRAY['JustSold', 'HomeSelling', 'RealEstateAgent', 'MovingOn', 'Sold'], NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/the-emotion-driven-just-sold/example1-the-emotion-driven-just-sold.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/the-emotion-driven-just-sold/example2-the-emotion-driven-just-sold.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/the-emotion-driven-just-sold/example3-the-emotion-driven-just-sold.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/the-emotion-driven-just-sold/example4-the-emotion-driven-just-sold.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/the-emotion-driven-just-sold/example5-the-emotion-driven-just-sold.png'], '[{"title":"Record the Video","body":""},{"title":"Export or Personalize Your Video","body":""}]', 'US', false, true);

