rovements are proven to deliver high returns on investment (ROI) without a full remodel. Whether you‚Äôre in Nashville or beyond, these tips are designed to give you the edge in a competitive market. Watch now to learn how you can make your home shine and maximize your sale price!', ARRAY['RealEstateTips', 'HomeSellingTips', 'HomeUpgrades', 'HomeImprovement', 'CurbAppeal', 'IncreaseHomeValue', 'RealEstateAdvice', 'HomeSellingGuide', 'NashvilleRealEstate', 'HouseForSale', 'SellingYourHome', 'RealEstateMarketing', 'ROI'], NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/votw-5-simple-upgrades-to-maximize-your-homes-value-before-selling-in-insert-area/example-votw-5-simple-upgrades-to-maximize-your-homes-value-before-selling-in-insert.png'], '[{"title":"Record the Video","body":""},{"title":"Create Your Thumbnail","body":""}]', 'US', false, true);

