VALUES ('VOTW: Zillow‚Äôs NEW Housing Market Forecast', 'votw-zillows-new-housing-market-forecast', '<p id="">This week‚Äôs video already has 45,000 views in less than 4 months. It‚Äôs a high-performing outlier video that can help establish you as an expert in your market. My recommendation is to personalize this video with data/insight from the market in your area to add your own hyper-local twist. </p><p id="">Here‚Äôs the <a href="https://www.zillow.com/research/home-value-sales-forecast-33822/">original link to the research conducted by Zillow</a></p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/votw-zillows-new-housing-market-forecast/thumbnail-votw-zillows-new-housing-market-forecast.png', true, 'reel', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGVgq93_GQ/x_jOKFHSBV8ll4vLFjnc5w/view?utm_content=DAGVgq93_GQ&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', 'Show Flow', 'https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/3idsw9zi2bino54mwc55j/Show-Flow-Zillow-s-NEW-Housing-Market-Forecast.pdf?rlkey=6wr3y662uboi9x4ik5os60iae&st=9i5ln6yv&dl=1', 'https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/nnd5od2o9jwmebfyofwfg/ElevenLabs_2024-11-04T15_10_02_Laura_pre_s50_sb75_se0_b_m2.mp3?rlkey=3w91gp73u7z7c8u21xjz87zyq&st=helfp09g&dl=1', NULL, 'Zillow‚Äôs NEW Housing Market Forecast (and what does it mean for <Insert AREA>)', 'Stay ahead of the real estate market with the latest forecast from Zillow! In this video, we dive deep into Zillow‚Äôs predictions for home values and sales across the country and explore what these trends mean for buyers and sellers in [local area]. Whether you‚Äôre planning to buy, sell, or invest, understanding these market shifts can help you make the right move. Watch to get insights on key cities, expected growth, inventory levels, and how these factors impact affordability. Don‚Äôt miss out on these valuable insights!', ARRAY['RealEstateMarket', 'HousingMarketForecast', 'ZillowReport', 'HomeValues', 'RealEstateTips', 'HousingTrends', 'MarketUpdate', 'RealEstateInvesting', 'HomeBuyingTips', 'LocalRealEstate'], NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/votw-zillows-new-housing-market-forecast/example-votw-zillows-new-housing-market-forecast.png'], '[{"title":"Record the Video","body":""},{"title":"Create Your Thumbnail","body":""}]', 'US', false, true);

