VALUES ('Why Pricing Your Home High Is A Risky Strategy', 'why-pricing-your-home-high-is-a-risky-strategy', '<p id="">Pricing your home too high might feel like a smart move‚Äîyou can always lower it later, right? But in reality, overpricing can do more harm than good.</p><p id="">The first week on the market is <em id="">everything.</em> That‚Äôs when serious buyers are searching, ready to make offers. But if your price is too high? You risk getting ignored, losing momentum, and ultimately selling for <em id="">less</em> than if you had priced it right from the start.</p><p id="">This carousel breaks down why overpricing is risky‚Äîand how to price strategically to attract strong offers.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/why-pricing-your-home-high-is-a-risky-strategy/thumbnail-why-pricing-your-home-high-is-a-risky-strategy.png', false, 'static_image', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGhCFOZB_s/mvKdbasOwpHEiaco511GPg/view?utm_content=DAGhCFOZB_s&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Social%20Shareables/why-pricing-your-home-high-is-a-risky-strategy/example-why-pricing-your-home-high-is-a-risky-strategy.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Post to Instagram","body":"<p><strong id=\"\">1. Start a New Post:</strong> Open Instagram and tap the <strong id=\"\">+</strong> icon to create a new post.<strong id=\"\">2. Select Carousel Format:</strong> Tap <strong id=\"\">Select Multiple</strong> (icon with stacked squares) to enable carousel posting.<strong id=\"\">3. Choose Your Images/Videos:</strong><strong id=\"\">4. Arrange Your Slides:</strong><ul id=\"\"><li>Drag and reorder the selected files to your preferred order.</li></ul><strong id=\"\">6. Write a Caption:</strong> Add a compelling caption to accompany your carousel.<strong id=\"\">7. Add Tags &amp; Location (Optional):</strong><ul id=\"\"><li>Tag people, add hashtags, and include a location if relevant.</li></ul><strong id=\"\">8. Share Your Post:</strong> Tap <strong id=\"\">Share</strong> to publish your carousel.<em id=\"\">See the image below to view how the carousel appears on your profile.</em></p><ol id=\"\"><li>Select up to 10 images or videos for your carousel.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

