VALUES ('35,234 people saw 36 Grant Drive', 'market-your-marketing', '<p id="">One of the best ways to turn your recent sales into more listings is to use a technique we call: <em id="">Market your marketing.</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">35,234 people saw this on Facebook</em> is an irresistible hook.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">This is more than just a success story, it''s proof that you''re great at your job.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">By highlighting a specific marketing metric, you demonstrate your ability to get their home in front of more prospective buyers‚Äîsomething sellers value a lot.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">So the next time you sell a home:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Take a single WOW metric from your advertising or marketing campaigns.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Send this email.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Then, record a video and share it on social media.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Then, mail a letter to nearby neighbors.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Rinse and repeat.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/market-your-marketing/thumbnail-market-your-marketing.png', '<p>35,234 people saw 36 Grant Drive</p>', '<p>A few weeks ago, I emailed you about our newest listing at 36 Grant Drive.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I wanted to circle back to give you a quick update:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>The home was listed for 12 days.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>We had 23 offers total (including 8 cash offers).</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>And it''s currently under contract for $28,345 above the asking price.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>To provide some perspective, that is an 8%&nbsp;higher sales-to-list ratio than comparable homes in our market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>How did we achieve such a great outcome for our client?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>We don''t just list our homes, we launch them.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>We invest thousands of dollars into preparing, staging, and marketing our clients'' homes because when it comes to selling your home, every dollar counts.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>If you missed out on 36 Grant Drive, don''t worry! I''ll keep you posted with updates on new homes hitting the market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Thank you,</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>[Your Name]</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['listing-promotions', 'soi', 'leads'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/market-your-marketing/example-market-your-marketing.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

