VALUES ('90% of Homeowners Are Concerned About This...', '90-of-homeowners-are-concerned-about-this', '<p id="">Staying connected with your sphere of influence (SOI) and keeping them informed about the latest market trends is a powerful strategy in real estate. By regularly updating your contacts on current events and market conditions, you not only provide valuable insights but also position yourself as a trusted advisor. This approach leads to more repeat and referral business, as satisfied clients are more likely to recommend you to their friends and family.</p><p id="">In this email, I want to address a pressing issue many homeowners face today‚Äîthe rising costs of insurance and taxes‚Äîand offer my expertise to help you navigate these challenges.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/90-of-homeowners-are-concerned-about-this/thumbnail-90-of-homeowners-are-concerned-about-this.png', '<p id="">90% of Homeowners Are Concerned About This‚Ä¶</p>', '<p id="">Hi [Client''s Name],</p><p id="">When clients call me to sell their home, it''s typically due to a life event‚Äîmarriage, divorce, needing more space, or job relocation. <br><br>However, more often these days, it''s due to the rising cost of insurance and taxes. <br><br>According to a HousingWire survey, 90% of homeowners are worried about these increasing costs.</p><p id="">If you''re not in your forever home and want to evaluate if selling makes sense, the first step is to see if there are new homes that fit both your criteria of "I want to live here" and "I can afford it."</p><p id="">Here''s how I help my clients navigate this market:</p><p id=""><strong id="">Market Analysis:</strong> I will provide you with a detailed analysis of your current home''s market value, so you have a clear understanding of what you can expect if you decide to sell.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Personalized Search:</strong> We''ll identify potential new homes that match your criteria, ensuring they are within your budget and in a location you love.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Financial Review:</strong> Together, we''ll look at your financial situation, including potential savings on insurance and taxes, to ensure your next move is financially sound.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Expert Guidance:</strong> I''ll guide you through every step of the selling and buying process, making it as smooth and stress-free as possible.</p><p id="">I''m not sure if this is for you, but if you''re feeling overwhelmed or confused and would value an expert second opinion, I''m here to help. <br><br>Simply reply to this email and we can schedule a 1-on-1 consultation. I look forward to hearing from you.</p><p id="">Best regards,<br>[Your Name]<br>[Your Contact Information]</p>', NULL, 'Seller Leads + SOI', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/90-of-homeowners-are-concerned-about-this/example-90-of-homeowners-are-concerned-about-this.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

