VALUES ('Days On Market Email', 'days-on-market-email', '<p id="">S/O to Jeremy Davis from <a href="https://palmagent.com/" id="">Palm Agent</a>.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you haven''t downloaded their app, they have a killer feature that allows you to calculate the holding cost based on the sales price.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If a home is on the market for 30 days, 60 days, 90 days, 120 days‚Äîhow much does it <em id="">actually</em> cost the consumer to have their property sit on the market?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Let''s say, for example, that a $725,000 home is on the market for 90 days. The holding costs could be upwards of $19,000-20,000.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Most sellers wouldn''t know that. In their mind, what''s the big deal if it''s 7 days or 45 days?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It matters because it could literally cost them thousands of dollars in equity they''ve earned.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This campaign is a great opportunity for you to communicate why your ability to sell a home quickly actually matters to the consumer.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/days-on-market-email/thumbnail-days-on-market-email.png', '<p>üòäüò•ü•µü§¨</p>', '<p id="">We sell homes faster than the average agent.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Why does this matter?</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs why‚Ä¶&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">When you list your home with an agent, the last thing you want to do is lose out on all of the equity you‚Äôve built because your home is sitting on the market.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Sure.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">You could accept a lowball offer.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">But we don‚Äôt think you should settle.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Every day that your home is sitting on the market with no viable offers, you‚Äôre losing money.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">How much? </p><p>‚Äç</p><p>///////////////// INSERT IMAGE /////////////////</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">So to the average agent, it might sound like overkill that we spend a tremendous amount of time preparing our clients'' homes for launch.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">But in our opinion, there''s no other option.<br><br>I‚Äôm not sure if you‚Äôre thinking about selling but if you‚Äôre open to the idea and you want to explore your options, I‚Äôd love to help.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Just call or text me at 555-555-555 to get started.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Sincerely,</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">John Smith</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['local-expert', 'direct-response', 'soi'], NULL, 'https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b3c5fd1ff8bd0fdc5ee861/65f0f4530ed2f6147a7309a2_image1.jpg', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/days-on-market-email/example-days-on-market-email.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

