VALUES ('EOTW: 12% Jump', 'eotw-12-jump', '<p id="">Your database is full of potential opportunities‚Äîbut only if you stay top-of-mind with the right message. This email taps into current market data to spark curiosity and engagement from homeowners, positioning you as the expert they can trust.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-12-jump/thumbnail-eotw-12-jump.png', '<p id="">Mortgage Applications Jump 12%: Is Now the Time to Sell?</p>', '<p id="">Hi [First Name],<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">CNBC recently reported a <strong id="">12% jump</strong> in mortgage applications.</p><p id="">At first glance, 12% might not seem like much‚Äîbut compared to the same time last year, that‚Äôs an <strong id="">increase of over 52%</strong>.</p><p id=""><strong id="">So, what does this mean for you?</strong></p><p id="">Two key takeaways:</p><ol id=""><li>Buyers have become <strong id="">more accepting</strong> of interest rates in the 6-7% range but remain highly sensitive to even small rate drops.<br><br></li><li>This shift could be good news for would-be sellers. It suggests the pool of buyers‚Äîespecially those keeping an eye on interest rates‚Äîmay be growing, making it a great time to consider listing your home.<br><br></li></ol><p id="">This surge could translate to <strong id="">more offers, faster sales, and potentially higher prices</strong> for sellers who position their homes strategically.</p><p id="">As always, I‚Äôm here to help you make sense of the market and how it affects your plans.</p><p id=""><strong id="">P.S.</strong> Has anyone sent you your <strong id="">2024 home value report</strong> yet? If not, reply to this email, and I‚Äôll create a <strong id="">professional, accurate report</strong> for you today. (It‚Äôs much more reliable than online tools!)</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-12-jump/example-eotw-12-jump.png', 