VALUES ('EOTW: Annual Value Report', 'eotw-annual-value-report', '<p id="">Nearly 30% of CMA request leads transact within 12 months. </p><p id="">That‚Äôs why sending the Home Value Email is the perfect way to end the year. Start building your Spring pipeline today using this campaign.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-annual-value-report/thumbnail-eotw-annual-value-report.png', '<p id="">Can I Prepare Your Annual Home Value Report?</p>', '<p id="">Hi [First Name],<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">Next week, I‚Äôm preparing personalized home value reports for my clients.<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">My clients love these reports because they provide an up-to-date, accurate assessment of their home‚Äôs value, using recent sales data and insights tailored to their property.<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">Can I prepare one for your home?<br>Sincerely,<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">P.S. Unlike online estimates, this report is customized specifically for your home, making it far more reliable.</p>', NULL, 'Leads (optional to include your SOI)', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-annual-value-report/example-eotw-annual-value-report.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

