VALUES ('EOTW: Bonus Black Friday Email', 'eotw-bonus-black-friday-email', '<p id="">I‚Äôm a huge fan of cross-promoting my social media content to my email list. So here‚Äôs what I want you to do ‚Äì when you post your Instagram Black Friday Carousel, send this email to your database and link them directly to IG. </p><p id="">This is a great way to grow your following and help your post go viral.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-bonus-black-friday-email/thumbnail-eotw-bonus-black-friday-email.png', '<p id="">Our Favorite Local Black Friday Deals</p>', '<p id="">Hi [First Name],<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you‚Äôre like us, you love supporting the community whenever possible.</p><p id="">To help all the amazing local businesses in our area, we‚Äôve put together a curated list of the best <strong id="">Black Friday</strong> deals in (INSERT AREA).</p><p id="">Check Them Out Now </p><p id="">Happy Holidays,</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database (Trust Me üòä )', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-bonus-black-friday-email/example-eotw-bonus-black-friday-email.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

