VALUES ('EOTW: Don‚Äôt call it a comeback', 'eotw-dont-call-it-a-comeback', '<p id="">Did you know that 70% of clients work with the first agent who stays top-of-mind? </p><p id="">Consistently reaching out to your database with relevant, valuable insights isn‚Äôt just about staying in touch‚Äîit‚Äôs about positioning yourself as the trusted expert they‚Äôll turn to when it‚Äôs time to buy or sell.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-dont-call-it-a-comeback/thumbnail-eotw-dont-call-it-a-comeback.png', '<p id="">Is the housing market bouncing back?</p>', '<p id="">I just read a report I thought was worth sharing:</p><p id="">Before elections, the housing market often freezes.</p><p id="">But once they‚Äôre over, we usually start to see early signs of what‚Äôs ahead.</p><p id="">Redfin‚Äôs Homebuyer Demand Index‚Äîa measure of tours and other buying services from Redfin agents‚Äîjumped more than 15% this past weekend, reaching its highest level in nearly a year and a half.</p><p id="">It‚Äôs too soon to predict exactly what will happen next year, but many experts are forecasting lower rates and increased home sales.</p><p id="">As always, I‚Äôll keep you updated on the latest market trends.<br>Sincerely,&nbsp;</p><p id="">P.S. I‚Äôm starting my annual home value check-ins for clients. These reports are more detailed and accurate than online tools. Would you like me to prepare one for your home?</p>', NULL, 'Leads (optional to include your SOI)', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-dont-call-it-a-comeback/example-eotw-dont-call-it-a-comeback.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

