VALUES ('EOTW: Jerome Powell', 'eotw-jerome-powell', '<p id="">In order to build trust and confidence with the consumer, you have to consistently deliver value. Part of our job as professional real estate agents is to keep the consumer informed on important updates. </p><p id="">So when Jerome Powell announces that a rate cut is imminent, it‚Äôs the perfect opportunity to engage our database with value.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-jerome-powell/thumbnail-eotw-jerome-powell.png', '<p id="">The News We‚Äôve Been Waiting For</p>', '<p id="">After what feels like forever, a rate cut in September is finally on the horizon.<br>How much?</p><p id="">That‚Äôs still up in the air, but here‚Äôs the deal:</p><p id="">A rate cut could spark a spike in buying demand.</p><p id="">That would likely lead to faster sales cycles, fewer price reductions and a rise in ‚Äúmultiple offers‚Äù scenarios. </p><p id=""><br>But here‚Äôs the twist‚Äîhomeowners who have been waiting to sell, clinging to their low-interest rates, might finally decide it‚Äôs time to move, bringing fresh listings to the market.</p><p id="">We could see more demand and more supply‚Äîa win-win for everyone.</p><p id="">As always, I‚Äôll keep you posted on all the important updates happening in real estate. <br>‚Äç</p><p id="">Sincerely,</p>', NULL, 'Database (SOI Optional)', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-jerome-powell/example-eotw-jerome-powell.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=