VALUES ('EOTW: Rent vs. Sell', 'eotw-rent-vs-sell', '<p id=""><strong>The best marketing speaks directly to the consumers needs and desires.&nbsp;</strong></p><p id="">According to a recent Zillow research study, Almost two thirds considered renting out their home before selling. About two thirds of sellers (66%) said they at least thought about renting out their home. A smaller share (28%), however, said they seriously considered renting out their home.&nbsp;</p><p id="">That‚Äôs why, we‚Äôve created the Rent vs. Sell email. It‚Äôs designed to start conversations with serious sellers. </p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-rent-vs-sell/thumbnail-eotw-rent-vs-sell.png', '<p id="">Rent Vs. Sell</p>', '<p id="">If you''re debating whether to sell or rent out your property, a professional <strong id="">Rent vs Sell Analysis</strong> can help.</p><p id="">This report breaks down:</p><ul id=""><li><strong id="">Estimated rental income</strong> you could earn annually.</li><li><strong id="">Net proceeds</strong> from a potential sale.</li></ul><p id="">It factors in local market trends and your property''s condition, giving you a clear picture of both options. Even if selling isn‚Äôt on your radar yet, it‚Äôs a valuable tool for future planning.</p><p id="">Would you like me to prepare a customized Rent vs Sell Analysis for your home?</p><p id="">I look forward to hearing from you.</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-rent-vs-sell/example-eotw-rent-vs-sell.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to Email Blast App","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

