VALUES ('EOTW: Where are all the foreclosures?', 'eotw-where-are-all-the-foreclosures', '<p id="">For this week‚Äôs featured email, we wanted to focus on controlling the narrative around the health of the housing market. Unfortunately, there is so much confusion and click-bait headlines around housing-crash that we had to set the record straight.&nbsp;</p><p id="">These emails are designed to engage your database, establish you as the market expert and build trust with your prospects.&nbsp;</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-where-are-all-the-foreclosures/thumbnail-eotw-where-are-all-the-foreclosures.png', '<p id="">Where are all the foreclosures?&nbsp;</p>', '<p id="">Hey there,</p><p id="">I had to reach out because there‚Äôs a lot of confusion about the current state of the housing market ‚Äì and I want to give you the real story.</p><p id="">In Q3 2024, lenders began the foreclosure process on just 62,380 properties across the U.S., which is <strong id="">down 10% from a year ago</strong>. <br><br>This figure is also well below pre-pandemic levels. <br><br>To put things into perspective, in 2019, foreclosure starts reached 335,985 ‚Äì and that was already a historic low since 2006.</p><p id="">So, when you see headlines hinting at a housing market crash, know the reality is different. <br><br>Yes, we‚Äôre facing affordability issues, rising costs of living, and a shortage of new homes.&nbsp;</p><p id="">But these challenges don‚Äôt necessarily indicate a 2008-style crisis.&nbsp;</p><p id="">The fundamentals of today‚Äôs market are much stronger.</p><p id="">As always, I‚Äôm here to keep you informed. If you have any questions or want to chat more about what‚Äôs happening in the market, feel free to reach out!</p>', NULL, 'Leads (optional to include your SOI)', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-where-are-all-the-foreclosures/example-eotw-where-are-all-the-foreclosures.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

