VALUES ('Email of the Week', 'email-of-the-week-3', '<p id="">Consistent communication is key to building trust and staying top-of-mind with your client.&nbsp;</p><p id="">This email campaign is designed to provide your clients with timely insights.</p><p id="">One quick pro-tip: When you send this email, you can track (within your CRM) who is opening the email. This is the PERFECT call list for your sales team.&nbsp;</p><p id="">When you bring value-based email marketing together with outbound sales, it‚Äôs magic.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/email-of-the-week-3/thumbnail-email-of-the-week-3.png', '<p id="">4 Stats You Should Know</p>', '<p id="">Hey [Client Name],</p><p id="">After reading this week‚Äôs Redfin market research, I wanted to share some highlights:</p><ol id=""><li><strong id="">Selling Below Asking:</strong> Homes sold for 0.3% less than asking in the four weeks ending June 23.</li><li><strong id="">Price Drops Rising:</strong> Nearly 7% of sellers dropped prices, the highest since November 2022.</li><li><strong id="">Stale Inventory:</strong> Over 60% of homes have been listed for at least a month without a contract.</li><li><strong id="">Buyers Hesitant:</strong> High housing costs and near 7% mortgage rates are causing buyers to pause. The median home-sale price hit a record $397,250.</li></ol><p id="">The one that stands out to me is <strong id="">stale inventory</strong>.</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs why:</p><p id="">If homes continue to sit on the market, motivated sellers may consider steep price reductions. <br><br>This could create opportunities for buyers to find their perfect home below market value.</p><p id="">I‚Äôm keeping an eye out and will keep you in the loop if anything pops up.</p><p id="">Let‚Äôs&nbsp;</p><p id="">p.s. If you‚Äôre a homeowner who‚Äôs concerned about rising taxes and insurance costs, reply to this email and I can prepare a professional home value report for you that can give you a sense of what your home would sell for in today‚Äôs market. </p><p>‚Äç</p>', NULL, 'Database (excluding SOI)', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/email-of-the-week-3/example-email-of-the-week-3.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

