VALUES ('Exclusivity Ends in 24 Hours', 'exclusivity-ends-in-24-hours', '<p id="">When you have a Coming Soon listing and you hit the 24 hours before it goes live, send this email.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s why it works so well:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">1. It creates urgency. The goal of the subject line, "Exclusivity ends in 24 hours" is to get as many people to open the email as possible.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">2. It piques curiosity. Share some info, but not all the info. Share one photo (the "money shot") but not all the photos.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">3. It has a strong CTA. Don''t drive them to a website. Get them to call.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/exclusivity-ends-in-24-hours/thumbnail-exclusivity-ends-in-24-hours.png', '<p>Exclusivity Ends in 24 Hours</p>', '<p>But per the MLS&nbsp;guidelines, I only have 24 hours to share this home with you before everyone can access it on Zillow.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>For location, price, and details, call my personal cell:&nbsp;555-555-5555.</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['listing-promotions', 'direct-response', 'soi', 'leads'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/exclusivity-ends-in-24-hours/example-exclusivity-ends-in-24-hours.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

