VALUES ('FSBO Email Campaign: This Is Where Most Sellers Get Stuck', 'fsbo-email-campaign-this-is-where-most-sellers-get-stuck', '<p id="">Most FSBO sellers think the hardest part is getting an offer. But in reality? The toughest part is knowing what to do next.</p><p id="">Many sellers assume price is all that matters. But once the offers start rolling in, they realize there‚Äôs a lot more at stake‚Äîhidden costs, contingencies, and tricky negotiations that can cost them thousands. The problem? FSBO sellers don‚Äôt always see these pitfalls coming until it‚Äôs too late.</p><p id="">This email positions you as the guide they didn‚Äôt know they needed. By educating them upfront and offering a free CMA, you‚Äôre not just providing value‚Äîyou‚Äôre giving them the clarity and confidence they won‚Äôt get from an online estimate. No sales pitch, just real help. And when they hit a roadblock? You might be the first person they think to call.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/fsbo-email-campaign-this-is-where-most-sellers-get-stuck/thumbnail-fsbo-email-campaign-this-is-where-most-sellers-get-stuck.png', '<p id="">Selling FSBO? This is where most sellers get stuck</p>', '<p id="">Selling a home is a big decision‚Äîwhether you go the For Sale By Owner (FSBO) route or work with an agent. Either way, there‚Äôs one moment that can catch sellers off guard: when the offers start coming in.</p><p id="">There‚Äôs a lot more to an offer than just the price. Things like:<br>‚úî <strong id="">Commissions, closing costs, and contingencies</strong>‚Äîhow much are you actually walking away with?<br>‚úî <strong id="">Negotiation pressure</strong>‚Äîwhen to counter, when to stand firm, and when to say no.</p><p id=""><strong id="">The best way to prepare? Knowing your home‚Äôs true market value.</strong></p><p id="">If you‚Äôre thinking about selling, I‚Äôd be happy to put together a <strong id="">Comparative Market Analysis (CMA)</strong> that shows what homes like yours are actually selling for‚Äînot just what online estimates say. It‚Äôs a simple way to make sure you‚Äôre pricing strategically and ready when buyers start making offers.</p><p id="">Would you like me to prepare one for your home?</p><p id="">Sincerely,</p><p id="">[Your Name]</p>', NULL, 'Prospects', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], 'Prospects', NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/fsbo-email-campaign-this-is-where-most-sellers-get-stuck/example-fsbo-email-campaign-this-is-where-most-sellers-get-stuck.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

