VALUES ('Favor', 'favor', '<p id="">We all know that reviews matter.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">But if we''re honest, most of us might miss the opportunity to capture the story and the sentiment from a happy client after the transaction.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">This is an email you can send to your past clients immediately after you help them complete the transaction.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">The best part?</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">It actually includes five questions to make it easier for them to leave a review.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Be sure to include the link to where they can write the review, right in the email.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">If you do success stories with your past clients, you can also use these questions in your interviews.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/favor/thumbnail-favor.png', '<p id="">Hi [Insert First Name],</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">I have a small favor to ask.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">I believe your story is worth sharing, and I''d love for you to take a moment to write about your experience working with us.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">You can write it here: [Your Team] on Google</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Your review matters because it helps future buyers and sellers make more informed decisions.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Thank you for taking the time to do this!</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>It really means the world to me.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Talk soon,</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>[Your Name]</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>p.s. Don''t worry if you don''t know what to write; I''ve included five simple questions to help you:</p><p>‚Äç</p><ol start="1"><li>Why did you decide to make a move?</li><li>What were you looking for in your Realtor?</li><li>Why did you choose us?</li><li>What did you value most about our service?</li><li>What advice would you give to a potential buyer or seller?</li></ol>', NULL, NULL, NULL, ARRAY['brand-building', 'past-clients'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/favor/example-favor.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

