VALUES ('Forward to a Friend', 'forward-to-a-friend', '<p id="">In his book <em id="">Viral Loop</em>, Adam L. Penenberg profiles the rise of Hotmail, and tells the story of how it happened.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">To help spread the word about Hotmail, they added this line...</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">"p.s. I Love You. Get a free email at Hotmail.com"&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">That small hook at the end of the message created a hockey stick growth for them.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">So here''s the zen learning‚Ä¶</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">The people in your database may not be buying today but they know someone who is.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">More importantly, they can introduce you to a new prospect with the right hook.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">The next time you have a listing to promote, try this email below.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/forward-to-a-friend/thumbnail-forward-to-a-friend.png', '<p>Forward to a Friend</p>', '<p>We''re about to list a property in the next 24 hours that I believe will sell within 7-10 days.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>The home is located in [area] and will be listed for [$].</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Forward this email to a friend who you know is in the market but hasn''t found a home yet.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Here''s my personal cell: 555-555-5555.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>They can call me directly and I can give them all the details before it hits the market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>[Your Name]</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>p.s. If I don''t pick up, be sure to leave a voicemail.</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['listing-promotions', 'soi', 'leads'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/forward-to-a-friend/example-forward-to-a-friend.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

