VALUES ('How much profit will you actually get if you sell your home?', 'net-sheet', '<p id="">This is something that isn''t talked about enough‚Äîhow much the seller will actually walk away with after the sale.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Use this script to provide incredible value to potential sellers.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Pro-Tip: PalmAgent ONE is a fantastic app to help you with Net Sheets estimates.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/net-sheet/thumbnail-net-sheet.png', '<p>How much profit will you actually get if you sell your home?</p>', '<p id="">Most people use tools like Zillow to find out how much their home is worth.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">But here''s something you might not know...</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">As a professional real estate agent, I can accurately calculate how much you will actually profit after a sale.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">This is called a Net Sheet.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I offer this as a free value add for all my clients.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Would you like one for your home?</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['soi', 'leads', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/net-sheet/example-net-sheet.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

