VALUES ('How to Navigate Uncertainty (CA)', 'how-to-navigate-uncertainty', '<p id="">It‚Äôs okay to feel uncertain right now. Your clients are feeling it, and if you‚Äôre being honest, you probably are too. The constant headlines‚Äîtrade tensions, tariffs, economic shifts‚Äîmake it hard to know what‚Äôs next. And when things feel unpredictable, it‚Äôs natural to hesitate.</p><p id="">But uncertainty doesn‚Äôt mean pressing pause. It means leaning into what <em id="">doesn‚Äôt</em> change‚Äîyour expertise, your ability to guide, and the trust you‚Äôve built with your clients. They don‚Äôt need all the answers right now. They just need someone who can help them understand their options and make decisions with confidence.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/how-to-navigate-uncertainty/thumbnail-how-to-navigate-uncertainty.png', '<p id="">How to navigate uncertainty</p>', '<p id="">The uncertainty around the U.S./Canada tariffs, the economy, and what it all means is unsettling.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Especially if you‚Äôre in the market to buy and/or sell.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">When things feel out of control, it‚Äôs easy to make decisions that are reactive.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">That‚Äôs why I‚Äôve been advising my clients to <em id="">take a deep breath</em>, and take a step back.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Because it‚Äôs times like these when we really need a strategic, well-thought-out plan to make the best decision.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">No matter what stage of the real estate planning process you‚Äôre in, if you‚Äôre looking for any guidance, I‚Äôm here to help.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Sincerely,</p><p id="">[Your Name]</p>', NULL, 'Prospects', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], 'Prospects', NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/how-to-navigate-uncertainty/example-how-to-navigate-uncertainty.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'CA', false, true);

