VALUES ('Just Sold: Should You Move Up Your Timeline to Sell?', 'ca-eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell-just-sold', '<p id="">Your clients look to you for real market insights‚Äînot headlines, not hearsay. Whenever you have a marketable moment‚Äîa real success story like a client selling above their online estimate or above ask‚Äîit‚Äôs a prime opportunity to send an email like this.&nbsp;</p><p id="">When homeowners see others achieving impressive results, they naturally start wondering, <em id="">‚ÄúCould that be me?‚Äù </em>That‚Äôs herd mentality in action‚Äîpeople are influenced by what others around them are doing, especially in uncertain times.&nbsp;</p><p id="">This email taps into that psychology, using a compelling example to shift homeowners from curiosity to action.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Customize the opening sentence with any stat from your client‚Äôs experience that demonstrates strong demand in your market.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/ca-eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell-just-sold/thumbnail-ca-eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell-just-sold.png', '<p id="">Should you move up your timeline to sell?</p>', '<p id="">I just had a client sell in 3 days for above the asking price.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">(I‚Äôm not exaggerating.)</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">I‚Äôve shared this news with a few of my clients and now they‚Äôre considering selling sooner than they originally planned.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Now, I know this doesn‚Äôt automatically mean that every home will sell that quickly or for over the asking price‚Äîevery home is different. But if you‚Äôre even a little curious about what this could mean for your home, the next step is to get a clearer picture of your home‚Äôs current market value.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Would you like me to prepare a personalized home value report for you?</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], 'Everyone', NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/ca-eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell-just-sold/example-ca-eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell-just-sold.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'CA', false, true);

