VALUES ('Off Market Opportunity Email', 'off-market-opportunity-email', '<p id="">If you have an off-market opportunity, this is the perfect email to send to your list of buyers.</p><p id="">Scarcity creates demand. The moment something feels exclusive‚Äîsomething others <em id="">can‚Äôt</em> have‚Äîit becomes even more desirable. Off-market properties tap into this psychology, but only if you position them the right way. The mistake most agents make? They focus only on the property itself. But buyers don‚Äôt just want a home‚Äîthey want an <em id="">edge</em>, too.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/off-market-opportunity-email/thumbnail-off-market-opportunity-email.png', '<p id="">Off-Market Deal [time sensitive]</p>', '<p id="">I just got the news about an off-market opportunity in <strong id="">[neighborhood]</strong> for under <strong id="">[$$$]</strong>.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Not many people know about it (yet).</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">This could be an unreal opportunity if you‚Äôre looking for:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><ul id=""><li><strong id="">[Feature 1]</strong></li><li><strong id="">[Feature 2]</strong></li><li><strong id="">[Feature 3]</strong></li></ul><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">If you want more details before anyone else, call or text me today.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs my personal cell: 555-555-5555.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Sincerely,</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">[Your Name]</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], 'Everyone', NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/off-market-opportunity-email/example-off-market-opportunity-email.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it