VALUES ('Ray Ellen Strategy', 'ray-ellen-strategy', '<p id="">One of the smartest ways you can use your email marketing tool is to cross-promote your social media posts.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This is one of my favorite strategies implemented by <a href="http://instagram.com/rayzorback" id="">Ray Ellen</a>.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s how it works:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">1. Find a notable listing in the MLS (or Off-Market).</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">2. Write a brief post about it on social media with a CTA to DM you if they''re interested.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">3. Send an email blast to your database LINKING to your social post.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This is something you could do SEVERAL times a month to generate inbound opportunities.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Ask Ray. It works.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/ray-ellen-strategy/thumbnail-ray-ellen-strategy.png', '<p>Did you see my latest post on Facebook?</p>', '<p>I posted to Facebook last night about a 4-bedroom foreclosure in one of the best neighborhoods in West Little Rock.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I''ve already received an overwhelming response.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Reply to this email if you''d like me to send you all the details. üôè</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Thank You,</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>[Your Name]</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['listing-promotions', 'direct-response', 'soi', 'leads'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/ray-ellen-strategy/example-1-ray-ellen-strategy.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

