VALUES ('Rent vs Sell', 'rent-vs-sell', '<p id="">You probably have potential sellers in your database who are curious about whether they''d benefit more from renting or selling.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">So, why not speak directly to this particular prospect and offer them a Rent vs Sell Analysis?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">You might be surprised with the responses you get.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/rent-vs-sell/thumbnail-rent-vs-sell.png', '<p>Rent vs Sell</p>', '<p>If you''re like most homeowners, you may be weighing the pros and cons of selling versus renting out your current property.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>If this describes your current situation, I recommend getting a professional Rent vs Sell Analysis.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>This report will provide you with a detailed breakdown of how much income you could generate each year if you decide to rent out your home, as well as an estimate of your net proceeds in the event of a sale.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>It takes into account factors such as local market trends and the condition of your property to give you an accurate picture of your options.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Even if you don''t have any plans to sell, this report will be helpful as you weigh your future options.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Would you like me to prepare a Rent vs Sell Analysis for your home?</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['leads', 'direct-response', 'soi'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/rent-vs-sell/example-rent-vs-sell.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

