VALUES ('Sale Of The Week', 'sale-of-the-week', '<p id="">In today‚Äôs competitive real estate market, staying top-of-mind with local homeowners is crucial for success. Our "Sale Of The Week" email campaign is designed to provide timely, hyper-local insights that homeowners can''t easily find online. By sharing detailed analysis of recent, noteworthy sales, like how quickly a home sold and the factors contributing to its swift sale, we help our clients (real estate agents) demonstrate their in-depth knowledge and expertise in their local market.</p><p id="">Each email is crafted to keep homeowners informed about important market trends, showcasing your ability to understand and navigate the current real estate landscape. This not only positions you as a market expert but also fosters trust and credibility among potential sellers.</p><p id="">The benefits of this strategy are threefold:</p><p id=""><strong>1. Top-of-Mind Awareness:</strong> By regularly sharing valuable information, you stay at the forefront of homeowners'' minds when they consider selling their homes.</p><p id=""><strong>2. Market Expertise: </strong>Highlighting your knowledge of local market trends establishes you as the go-to real estate professional in your area.</p><p id=""><strong>3. New Listing Opportunities: </strong>The seller-centric call-to-actions (CTAs) encourage homeowners to reach out for professional home value reports and consultations, creating potential new listings.</p><p id="">By leveraging this campaign, you can effectively engage with your audience, build stronger relationships, and ultimately, generate more listing opportunities.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/sale-of-the-week/thumbnail-sale-of-the-week.png', '<p>Sale Of The Week: Why Did 323 South River Road Sell So Quickly?</p>', '<p>I just finished analyzing all 35 sales in Bedford, NH, and I came across a sale that I just had to share.</p><p>323 South River Road was on the market for less than 24 hours.</p><p>With 4.5 months of inventory (that‚Äôs up 70% since 2021) and most homes sitting on the market for 40-50 days, it‚Äôs uncommon in our area to see homes selling in less than one day.</p><p>I did some recon for you and talked to the listing agent.</p><p>They had 9 offers within the first 12 hours.</p><p>Here are three reasons why I believe this home sold so quickly:</p><p><strong>Competitive Pricing</strong>: The home was priced well at $799,000. For our area, any home between $700,000 and $900,000 attracts a lot of attention. In fact, this home had over 1,530 views on Zillow.</p><p><strong>Desirable Upgrades:</strong> The homeowner made several upgrades that buyers love ‚Äì an upgraded kitchen, renovated bathrooms, and beautiful landscaping. The curb appeal was spot on.</p><p><strong>Prime Location:</strong> Located 5 minutes from Bedford High School and less than 10 minutes from Whole Foods.</p><p>As always, I‚Äôm here to keep you informed about what‚Äôs happening in the market.</p><p>If you have any questions, feel free to text or call me anytime.</p><p>My personal cell is 555-555-5555<br>Jimmy Mackin</p><p>P.S. I just did a professional home value report for my client. They gained $130,000 in the last 18 months. They were shocked because their Zestimate said their home was worth $50,000 less. If you want a report for your home, just text me at 555-555-5555.</p>', NULL, 'Buyer and Seller leads', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/sale-of-the-week/example-sale-of-the-week.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

