VALUES ('Seller Activation Email', 'seller-activation-email-2', '<p id="">One of the most effective ways to generate high-quality seller leads is through targeted, personalized outreach‚Äîlike the email you‚Äôre about to send to your database. When you share real success stories, such as a client‚Äôs home value increasing by $27,500 in just eight months, you‚Äôre doing more than just marketing‚Äîyou‚Äôre offering tangible proof of the value you can bring.</p><p id="">Be sure to personalize this message with a real-world example of a CMA you completed for a client.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/seller-activation-email-2/thumbnail-seller-activation-email-2.png', '<p id="">$27,500 in 8 months.</p>', '<p id="">I just completed a home value report for my client who has already gained $27,500 this year.</p><p id="">These reports are more comprehensive and accurate than what you''d get from an online tool.</p><p id="">Can I send you one for your home?</p><p id="">Let me know!</p><p id="">Sincerely,</p><p id="">Jimmy</p>', NULL, 'Database (Include SOI)', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/seller-activation-email-2/example-seller-activation-email-2.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

