VALUES ('Selling is a bad idea', 'selling-is-a-bad-idea', '<p id="">The thought "selling is a bad idea" has crossed the mind of nearly every seller at some point.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Rather than resorting to the usual "now is a good time to sell" pitch often used by Realtors, let''s tackle the issue directly.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">Selling your home is painful.</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">It''s emotional.</p><p id="">It can be overwhelming.</p><p id="">And it costs $$$.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Even when it''s easy, it''s not.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">There''s an adage in marketing, a small admission is how you gain large acceptance.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">So let''s address the pain head-on.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">This campaign can also be used for a direct mail letter and a short-form video on social media.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/selling-is-a-bad-idea/thumbnail-selling-is-a-bad-idea.png', '<p>Selling is a bad idea.</p>', '<p>Homeowners use a lot of words to describe selling...</p><p>‚Äç</p><p><em>Fun</em> isn''t typically one of them.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>It''s stressful. It''s complicated. It takes time. Strangers walk through your house and touch your stuff. Then you have to move all your stuff. The deal could come together, and then fall apart at the last minute.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>The list goes on.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>But here''s the thing...</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>When it''s time to sell, <em>you know.</em></p><p>‚Äç</p><p>In fact, a lot of homeowners in our area sold just in the last month.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Why?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>They wanted to upgrade. They wanted less maintenance. They wanted new neighbors. They wanted no neighbors. They wanted to move closer to (or farther away from) family.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>If you know it''s time to sell, we have a plan for your situation. Even if...</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>- Your home needs repairs.</p><p>- You live out of state.</p><p>- You really want to buy your next home before you sell</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>We have a solution for you.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Reply "sell" to this email and let''s have a conversation.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>[Your Name]</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['brand-building', 'soi', 'leads'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/selling-is-a-bad-idea/example-selling-is-a-bad-idea.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

