VALUES ('Serious Buyers Only', 'serious-buyers-only-us', '<p id="">If you want to attract serious buyers, your messaging needs to be clear, direct, and laser-focused on their goals. Think of this campaign as Part I of the Magic Buyer Strategy, which answers the critical question: <em id="">How do you find serious buyers?</em> The key is to highlight what most buyers don‚Äôt know‚Äîlike the fact that 1.2 million U.S. home sales in 2024 happened off-market, roughly 24% of all transactions.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Pro tip: if you sell a significant percentage of homes off-market, replace the national stat with your own for even greater impact.</p><p id="">This campaign‚Äôs goal is to get serious buyers to raise their hand by showing them you have access to opportunities they can‚Äôt find on their own.</p><p id="">To build credibility, include a recent buyer testimonial in the P.S. This reinforces your results and shows prospects the value of working with you.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/serious-buyers-only-us/thumbnail-serious-buyers-only-us.png', '<p>Serious buyers only <strong id=""><em id="">(offer inside) </em></strong></p>', '<p id="">If you‚Äôre just starting the homebuying process and need guidance, I‚Äôm here for you. Always happy to provide advice or answer questions.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id=""><strong id="">But this email is only for serious buyers who want an edge in this market.</strong></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs something most people don‚Äôt realize: the home you‚Äôre searching for might never make it to Zillow. In fact, roughly 24% of homes are sold off-market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">That‚Äôs why I offer a specialized service to help my clients source deals that you‚Äôll never find online.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This is a highly personalized approach, and to maintain its quality, I can only offer it to a select number of clients each month.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">So if you‚Äôre qualified, ready to move, and tired of scrolling through overpriced homes on Zillow, reply to this email with your:</p><ol id=""><li id="">Ideal Location</li><li id="">Price Range</li><li id="">Desired Move In Date</li><li id="">Minimum Bed / Bath Requirements</li><li id="">Any other must-haves&nbsp;</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Talk soon,<br>[Your Name]</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">‚Äç<em id="">P.S. My client Mary received this exact email 45 days ago. After spending 7.5 months searching for homes, we were able to source her an off-market deal that she loved in less than 33 days.</em></p><p id="">‚Äç<em id="">Here‚Äôs what she had to say about her experience: [testimonial]</em></p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/serious-buyers-only-us/example-serious-buyers-only-us.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

