VALUES ('Should I Sell This Summer?', 'should-i-sell-this-summer', '<p id="">One of the challenges that comes with real estate marketing is finding thousands of different ways to ask the consumer: "Are you considering selling soon?"</p><p id="">For this campaign, we''re using the "What''s holding you back" angle to get potential sellers to raise their hand.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s why it works:</p><p id="">1. The email opens with a relevant hook about how more sellers are entering the market.‚Ä®Pro-tip: Localize the inventory data for your market.</p><p id="">2. Including "Out of curiosity" softens the ask.</p><p id="">3. Multiple choice makes it easy to answer.</p><p id="">4. It includes a compelling p.s. with a relevant CTA for a home value report.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Put it to work.üëá</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/should-i-sell-this-summer/thumbnail-should-i-sell-this-summer.png', '<p>Should I Sell This Summer?</p>', '<p id="">If you''re confused, you''re not alone.<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">Many of my clients reach out to ask for help in making sense of this frustratingly foggy market.<br>- Should I sell?<br>- Should I wait?<br>- Are interest rates going to drop?</p><p id="">‚Äç<br>Predicting the market is tough, but we do have valuable insights to share.</p><p id="">‚Äç<br>Right now, we have nearly 30% more homes on the market in 2024 compared to 2023. </p><p id="">You might be surprised to learn that in the last week of April, we saw more homes hit the market than in any other week in 2023.</p><p id="">‚Äç<br><strong>Here''s what we do know:<br></strong>‚Äç</p><p id="">Experts are predicting that the number of homes hitting the market will continue to rise. It may take another 18-24 months before we see the same number of homes for sale as we saw in 2019.<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">This will most certainly have an impact on how much your home appreciates in value.<br>But here‚Äôs the thing: real estate is hyper-local.<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">We‚Äôre still seeing homes sell off-market before they even hit the MLS, and at the same time, we‚Äôre seeing homes sit on the market for 90+ days.<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">Bottom line: It''s important to stay up-to-date with your home''s value.<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">If it‚Äôs been a while since you‚Äôve had a professional home value report completed, simply reply with your address and I can prepare a complimentary report today.</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['leads'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/should-i-sell-this-summer/example-should-i-sell-this-summer.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

