VALUES ('Should You Move Up Your Timeline to Sell?', 'eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell', '<p id="">Your clients look to you for real market insights‚Äînot headlines, not hearsay.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Right now, you have a chance to control the narrative and provide clarity in a time of uncertainty.&nbsp;</p><p id="">In some markets, buyer activity is picking up, and well-priced homes are moving‚Äîeven with rates around 7%.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Use this email to guide homeowners toward an informed decision.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Send it as-is or make it even stronger by adding local data‚Äîlike the number of buyer appointments you‚Äôve scheduled‚Äîto reinforce your point.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell/thumbnail-eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell.png', '<p id="">Should you move up your timeline to sell?</p>', '<p id="">My calendar is filling up with buyer appointments.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It‚Äôs not how I expected February to start, but‚Ä¶I see it as a positive signal for the market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">And you should, too.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Even with rates hovering around 7%, buyers are motivated, homes priced well are selling fast, and we‚Äôre even seeing multiple offers.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">So if you know you want to sell in the next few years, it‚Äôs worth asking:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">"Could moving up my timeline help me price my home more competitively and still maximize its value?"</em></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">That‚Äôs exactly what I‚Äôm helping my clients figure out. I do this by providing a clear picture of the market‚Äîshowing what similar homes are selling for, helping them understand what buyers want, and crafting a plan to position their home to maximize value and timing.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you‚Äôre open to the idea of selling, would it be helpful if we connected for 15-20 minutes sometime this week?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">I‚Äôd love to answer any questions you have and help you feel confident about your next steps.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Sincerely,<br>[Your Name]</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], 'Everyone', NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell/example-eotw-should-you-move-up-your-timeline-to-sell.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

