VALUES ('Spring Housing Demand', 'eotw-spring-housing-demand-us', '<p id="">Is spring housing demand already starting?<br></p><p id="">According to HousingWire lead analyst Logan Mohtashami, the answer is yes.<br></p><p id="">In a recent article and interview with Yahoo Finance, Mohtashami highlighted a 2.2% rise in U.S. pending home sales in November‚Äîa strong signal that buyers are beginning to adapt to current market conditions and act earlier than usual.<br></p><p id="">While the traditional spring market may still feel a few months away, this trend underscores how critical it is for buyers to prepare now. Being ready with financing, pre-approval, and a solid strategy ensures they can act quickly when the perfect home comes along‚Äîand that‚Äôs where you come in.<br></p><p id="">As their trusted advisor, your expertise can guide them through every step of the process, from understanding the market to securing their dream home. This campaign emphasizes how your role is vital in helping buyers navigate the market and succeed this spring.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-spring-housing-demand-us/thumbnail-eotw-spring-housing-demand-us.png', '<p id="">Spring housing demand‚Ä¶has already started?</p>', '<p id="">We know‚Ä¶</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It feels way too early to start talking about the spring market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">But it‚Äôs here. Sort of.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">We‚Äôre seeing buyers settle into the current housing environment, and moving anyway.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">In fact, more homes are in contract now versus the same time last year‚Äîeven with higher mortgage rates.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><strong id="">Here‚Äôs why this matters:</strong></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">The ‚Äúspring market‚Äù as most people think of it might still be a couple months away, but it‚Äôs never too soon to get prepared.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><strong id="">Why?</strong></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Because when the perfect home hits the market, you want to be ready. Not scrambling to find a lender, or to get pre-approved, or to put together an offer.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Those are the buyers who will win in the spring market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you‚Äôd like to talk about your plans‚Äîor even just explore what‚Äôs possible‚ÄîI‚Äôm here to help!</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Sincerely,<br>[Your Name]</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">p.s. Not looking to buy but know someone who is? Forward this email to a friend who‚Äôs mentioned moving in 2025. They can text me directly at XXX-XXX-XXXX and I can help them get prepared‚Äîwhether they want to buy tomorrow, next month, or 4+ months from now.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-spring-housing-demand-us/example-eotw-spring-housing-demand-us.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', true, true);

