VALUES ('The #1 Thing Buyers Can Do To Get Ahead (CA)', 'the-1-thing-buyers-can-do-to-get-ahead-ca', '<p id="">With new listings surging across Canada‚Äîan 11% jump in January alone, the biggest supply increase since the 1980s‚Äîbuyers have more options than they‚Äôve seen in years (Financial Post). But more inventory doesn‚Äôt mean an easier search. It means competition, faster-moving deals, and the need to act decisively when the right home appears.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">This campaign gives you a simple, strategic way to guide buyers through the three key steps that separate those who hesitate from those who close. Use it to position yourself as the expert who helps buyers move with confidence.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/the-1-thing-buyers-can-do-to-get-ahead-ca/thumbnail-the-1-thing-buyers-can-do-to-get-ahead-ca.png', '<p>The #1 thing buyers can do to get ahead</p>', '<p id="">If you‚Äôre circling the market, waiting for the right home‚Ä¶</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs my advice: <strong id="">The sooner you can get prepared, the better off you‚Äôll be.&nbsp;</strong></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">We‚Äôre seeing an <strong id="">unprecedented surge in new listings across Canada</strong>‚Äîwith January recording an 11% month-over-month jump, the biggest leap in new supply since the 1980s (source: Financial Post). More inventory means <strong id="">more choices for buyers</strong>, but it also means a shifting market where preparation is key.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">That‚Äôs why I always encourage my buyers to do three simple things now:</p><ul id=""><li id=""><strong id="">Talk to a lender and get pre-approved</strong>‚Äîit helps you understand what you can truly afford.</li><li id=""><strong id="">Narrow your search criteria</strong>‚Äîso you recognize ‚Äúthe one‚Äù when you see it.</li><li id=""><strong id="">Stay close to the market</strong>‚Äîhomes can list midweek and sell before the weekend (it <em id="">does</em> happen).</li></ul><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Preparation gives you options‚Äîand peace of mind.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">As always, if you want to talk through any of this, I‚Äôm here.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Sincerely,</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">[Your Name]</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">P.S. If you‚Äôre already qualified, ready to move, and want to discuss next steps, just reply to this email‚Äîlet‚Äôs chat. üëã</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], 'Everyone', NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/the-1-thing-buyers-can-do-to-get-ahead-ca/example-the-1-thing-buyers-can-do-to-get-ahead-ca.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'CA', false, true);

