VALUES ('This chart says it all', 'anti-buy-now-eotw', '<p id="">Email marketing is the highest ROI marketing channel but you can‚Äôt just sell all the time. Instead, you have to figure out ways to keep your audience informed and engaged ‚Äì all while building trust. <br><br>So this email is designed to be the ANTI-Buy NOW email.&nbsp;The reality is, consumers are facing historic affordability challenges. <br><br>Say that. <br><br>It builds trust and confidence with the consumer. <br><br>No more date the rate and marry the house nonsense. </p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/anti-buy-now-eotw/thumbnail-anti-buy-now-eotw.png', '<p id="">This chart says it all</p>', '<p id="">There‚Äôs no question that buying a house remains a challenge.</p><p id=""><strong id="">But just how challenging?</strong></p><figure class="w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-normal" data-rt-type="image" data-rt-align="normal"><div><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b3c5fd1ff8bd0fdc5ee861/66d5d8bcb137707a333e4026_AD_4nXeBo5e2jioMRklqdep6HQAeixz1wNKE4TQj2USLlhkQk7-vwidsfB3L9iiifhhsjfY3gZsmFN9lREYHgINANUllpsZfsRVbsACnpDO1bokOxsBifgQ2wdZTjJ3F_KSsH5xqqX5C2kM7X78jYyC1OyWXK0u8.jpeg" width="auto" height="auto" alt="" loading="auto" id=""></div></figure><p id="">The chart below offers a historical perspective on the down payment needed to buy a home and the affordability of average mortgage payments.</p><p id="">Right now, down payments are at an all-time high, and affordability (measured by the percentage of median income) remains near record levels.</p><p id=""><strong id="">But there is a silver lining:</strong></p><p id="">Inventory has steadily increased over the last 24 months, and all signs point toward mortgage rates in the 5‚Äôs by early 2025.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Here‚Äôs my advice:</strong></p><p id=""><strong id="">Stay ready.</strong></p><p id="">The market has shifted from a speed-driven frenzy ‚Äî where it was all about rushing offers, waiving inspections, and hoping to win the real estate lottery.</p><p id="">Now, you have time.</p><p id="">You can carefully assess properties, gather all the information, and make informed decisions.</p><p id=""><strong id="">That‚Äôs a good thing.</strong></p><p id="">As always, I''m here to keep you updated on market trends. <br><br>If there‚Äôs anything I can do for you, just reply to this email.</p><p id="">Looking forward to helping you navigate these changes.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/anti-buy-now-eotw/example-anti-buy-now-eotw.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

