VALUES ('Timing the Market (CA)', 'timing-the-market-ca', '<p id="">Your clients want to time the market. The perfect moment to sell. The lowest rate to buy. It feels like the smart move‚Äîlike they‚Äôre outmaneuvering everyone else.&nbsp;</p><p id="">But here‚Äôs the uncomfortable truth you need to help them see: trying to time the market often costs more than it saves.&nbsp;</p><p id="">The pros‚Äîlike you‚Äîknow the market isn‚Äôt something to predict; it‚Äôs something to work with.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Your job is to shift their focus: does making a move this year align with their life and goals? This email will help you start that conversation.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/timing-the-market-ca/thumbnail-timing-the-market-ca.png', '<p id="">Should you try to time the market?</p>', '<p id="">When I look at the real estate market, I see a surge in new listings. I see more buyers coming off the sidelines with more choices available.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">And as helpful as it is to know that, no‚Äîthe market isn‚Äôt frozen, <em id="">yes</em>, people are buying and selling real estate every single day‚Ä¶that data doesn‚Äôt really help you answer this:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">Is 2025 the best time to sell MY house? Is 2025 the best time for ME to buy?</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">The truth is‚Äîyou‚Äôll never be able to time the market.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Whether or not you should buy or sell this year depends on what‚Äôs right for your situation:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">Can I comfortably cover my mortgage?</em></p><p id=""><em id="">Do I have enough equity to cover moving costs?</em></p><p id=""><em id="">Am I ready for the stress of moving?</em></p><p id=""><em id="">Do my long-term goals support a change?</em></p><p id=""><em id="">Is there a clear plan for my next home?</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Don‚Äôt rely on the news, or Reddit threads, or community Facebook pages to help you make real estate decisions.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">If you need any guidance on your situation, call or text me anytime at 555-555-5555, and I‚Äôd be happy to help you explore your options.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Sincerely,</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">[Your Name]</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], 'Everyone', NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/timing-the-market-ca/example-timing-the-market-ca.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'CA', false, true);

