VALUES ('What''s holding you back?', 'whats-holding-you-back', '<p id="">One of the challenges that comes with real estate marketing is finding thousands of different ways to ask the consumer: "Are you considering selling soon?"</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">For this campaign, we''re using the "What''s holding you back" angle to get potential sellers to raise their hand.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s why it works:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">1. The email opens with a relevant hook about how more sellers are entering the market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Pro-tip: Localize the inventory data for your market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">2. Including "Out of curiosity" softens the ask.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">3. Multiple choice makes it easy to answer.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">4. It includes a compelling p.s. with a relevant CTA for a home value report.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Put it to work.üëá</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/whats-holding-you-back/thumbnail-whats-holding-you-back.png', '<p>What''s holding you back from selling?</p>', '<p id="">This year, we''ve already seen a wave of new homes hit the market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">In fact, we''re up 107% from 2021.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Out of curiosity‚Äîwhat''s holding you back from selling?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">1. I''m actually ready to start the process.</p><p id="">2. I''m waiting for interest rates to drop.</p><p id="">3. I''m in my forever home. I''m never selling.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">I can''t wait to hear your answer.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Best,</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>[Your Name]</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">p.s. We just sold a home for [$] above its Zestimate. If it''s been a while since you''ve checked your home''s value with a professional, just reply to this email with your address, and I can prepare a report for you ASAP.</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['conversation-starters', 'past-clients', 'soi', 'cmas'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/whats-holding-you-back/example-whats-holding-you-back.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

