VALUES ('What''s your plan? [Land & Expand]', 'whats-your-plan', '<p id="">This is a strategy we call "Land &amp; Expand."</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It''s a technique to bridge the gap between marketing and sales. Which means, you''ll send a marketing email to a targeted list with a targeted message. Then follow-up with a text:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">Hi [First Name],&nbsp;</em></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">Hope you‚Äôre well my friend. I just sent you an email.&nbsp;</em></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">Let me know if you fall into bucket #1, #2 or #3 üôè</em></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Chances are they''ll get the text before they see your email. So you''ll start the conversation via text, prompt them to check their email, and hopefully respond to your text to continue the conversation.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">The goal of this strategy is to get a good sense of where your past clients fall in their seller journey as you think about your sales pipeline.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Are they 6-12 months out from selling?</p><p id="">2-4 years from now?</p><p id="">Maybe more?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">As you get more information and more context about their plans, add those notes to your CRM and start to be helpful right now to help them achieve whatever it is they want to achieve this year.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/whats-your-plan/thumbnail-whats-your-plan.png', '<p>What''s your plan?</p>', '<p>Hi [First Name],</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I''m reaching out because a lot of my clients are starting to think about their next move, and I wanted to see where you''re at.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Which of these would you consider to be your current situation?</p><p>‚Äç</p><ol start="1"><li>No plans‚ÄîI love my home!</li><li>I''m thinking about buying but haven''t found anything yet</li><li>I''m curious how much I could sell for</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p><p>Looking forward to your response! üôè</p>', NULL, NULL, ARRAY['soi', 'past-clients', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/whats-your-plan/example-whats-your-plan.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to Your Email Blast App","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

INSERT INTO email_campaigns (name, slug, introduction, thumbnail_url, subject_line, email_body, preview_text, target_audience, tags, recommended_audience, example_image_url, full_email_image_url, execution_steps, region, is_featured, is_active)
VALUES ('What‚Äôs next? (CA)', 'whats-next', '<p id="">Most agents think trust is built in big moments‚Äîan incredible listing presentation, a perfectly staged home, a well-executed negotiation. But trust isn‚Äôt a switch you flip. It‚Äôs a slow burn. It‚Äôs built in the moments when you‚Äôre not selling, just showing up with value.</p><p id="">That‚Äôs what this email does. No push. No pressure. Just sharp market insights your clients will appreciate. Over time, these touchpoints add up. They create familiarity, confidence, and‚Äîwhen the time is right‚Äîa listing opportunity.</p><p id=""><strong id="">ListingLeads member Anthony Malafronte saw it firsthand:</strong></p><p id=""><em id="">"Three new listings are coming on in the next couple of weeks! All using these tools and tactics. One we cultivated through email only, the owner is hearing impaired (the best listing appointment I have ever been on), I''m not sure we''d have made it happen without this group. When we met, the owner felt comfortable with our commitment to the business, our knowledge of the market, and our ability to market his home. The consistency with which we shared info, and weren''t annoying but smart and helpful. Was what he shared with us."</em></p><p id="">This email was crafted by pulling insights from recent articles in <em id="">The Financial Post, The Globe &amp; Mail,</em> and <em id="">BNN Bloomberg.</em> The Bank of Canada has cut rates seven times, yet demand hasn‚Äôt surged to match. Buyers are cautious, and the market is shifting in ways that create new opportunities.</p><p id="">Staying in front of your clients with timely, relevant insights is how you build trust‚Äîlong before they‚Äôre ready to make a move.</p><p id="">Let‚Äôs get into it.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/whats-next/thumbnail-whats-next.png', '<p id="">What‚Äôs next?</p>', '<p id="">The Bank of Canada just made its seventh consecutive rate cut, bringing the key rate down to 2.75%. With more cuts expected, mortgage rates could drop even further.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">At the same time, new listings have surged, giving buyers more choice‚Äîand in some cases, more negotiating power. Multiple offers are becoming less common, and for buyers who‚Äôve been waiting on the sidelines, this could be the opening they‚Äôve been hoping for.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">But so far, demand hasn‚Äôt surged to match. Inflation, trade tensions, and job security concerns are making some buyers hesitant. Many are waiting to see if rates drop further or if the economy stabilizes before making a move.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">What happens next will depend on how much further rates drop, whether buyers regain confidence, and how economic pressures‚Äîlike inflation and employment‚Äîplay out in the coming months.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">As always, I‚Äôm here to keep you informed. And if you have any questions, I‚Äôm here.</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], 'Everyone', NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/whats-next/example-whats-next.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'CA', false, true);

INSERT INTO email_campaigns (name, slug, introduction, thumbnail_url, subject_line, email_body, preview_text, target_audience, tags, recommended_audience, example_image_url, full_email_image_url, execution_steps, region, is_featured, is_active)
VALUES ('Why 2025 Might Be the Year to Buy A Home (CA)', 'eotw-why-2025-might-be-the-year-to-buy-a-home', '<p id="">‚ÄúIf you are considering buying, it is time to get busy.‚Äù Those are the words of Ted Rechtshaffen, President of TriDelta Financial, in a recent <em id="">Financial Post</em> article. His perspective highlights a key opportunity: today‚Äôs market conditions may offer buyers significant advantages that won‚Äôt last.</p><p id="">This email pulls data from The Canadian Real Estate Association (CREA) to explain why 2025 could be the year to make a move‚Äîand that‚Äôs where you come in.</p><p id="">As their trusted advisor, your expertise can guide them through every step of the process, from understanding the market to securing their dream home. This campaign emphasizes how your role is vital in helping buyers navigate the market and succeed this spring.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-why-2025-might-be-the-year-to-buy-a-home/thumbnail-eotw-why-2025-might-be-the-year-to-buy-a-home.png', '<p id="">5 reasons why 2025 might be the year to buy a home</p>', '<p id="">It‚Äôs true.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you‚Äôre considering buying a home, today‚Äôs prices could look cheap a year from now.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id=""><strong id="">Here‚Äôs why:</strong></p><ol id=""><li id=""><strong id="">Home prices are predicted to rise 4.4% this year </strong>(Canadian Real Estate Association): Buying now could save you thousands in the long run.</li></ol><ol start="2" id=""><li id=""><strong id="">Mortgage rates are lower:</strong> The Bank of Canada cut rates by 1.75% last year, making borrowing more affordable (Canadian Real Estate Association).</li></ol><ol start="3" id=""><li id=""><strong id="">Easier financing options:</strong> Insured mortgages now cover homes up to $1.5M, allowing buyers to qualify with as little as 5% down (Financial Post).</li></ol><ol start="4" id=""><li id=""><strong id="">Demand is growing</strong>: After two years of flat prices, buyers who‚Äôve been waiting on the sidelines are ready to act. Competition is heating up quickly.</li></ol><ol start="5" id=""><li id=""><strong id="">Immigration is driving the market</strong>: Canada‚Äôs 2025 immigration target of nearly 400,000 new residents adds strong, sustained demand for housing.</li></ol><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><strong id="">Here‚Äôs why this matters:</strong></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It‚Äôs never too soon to get prepared. The right home doesn‚Äôt wait‚Äîespecially in a market that‚Äôs gaining momentum. Having your financing in order, understanding your options, and knowing your next steps will make all the difference when the time comes.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you‚Äôd like to talk about your plans‚Äîor even just explore what‚Äôs possible‚ÄîI‚Äôm here to help. Let‚Äôs map out a strategy that fits your goals, your timeline, and your vision for 2025.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Sincerely,<br>[Your Name]</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">p.s. Not looking to buy but know someone who is? Forward this email to a friend who‚Äôs mentioned moving in 2025. They can text me directly at XXX-XXX-XXXX and I can help them get prepared‚Äîwhether they want to buy tomorrow, next month, or 4+ months from now.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/eotw-why-2025-might-be-the-year-to-buy-a-home/example-eotw-why-2025-might-be-the-year-to-buy-a-home.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'CA', true, true);

INSERT INTO email_campaigns (name, slug, introduction, thumbnail_url, subject_line, email_body, preview_text, target_audience, tags, recommended_audience, example_image_url, full_email_image_url, execution_steps, region, is_featured, is_active)
VALUES ('You might regret reading this', 'you-might-regret-reading-this', '<p id="">If you want to grab attention and convert curiosity into action, this campaign is your blueprint.</p><p id="">It‚Äôs built around three powerful marketing tactics designed to engage and persuade: Small Agreements, Objection Handling, and the Power of a Client Case Study.</p><p id="">By inviting homeowners to take a simple, no-pressure step‚Äîlike texting for a free home value report‚Äîit lowers barriers, builds trust, and encourages incremental commitment.</p><p id="">At the same time, it proactively addresses a common objection: ‚ÄúI don‚Äôt want to sell my home,‚Äù reframing the conversation to focus on clarity and future possibilities.</p><p id="">Including a real client success story‚Äîselling a home for $25,000 over Zestimate‚Äîadds credibility and proves your expertise, making your offer even more compelling.</p><p id="">Together, these strategies create a message that inspires action and helps you win your next listing.</p><p id="">Pro-Tip: Add your client‚Äôs testimonial in the P.S. to build even more credibility and trust.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/you-might-regret-reading-this/thumbnail-you-might-regret-reading-this.png', '<p id="">You might regret reading this</p>', '<p id="">If you love everything about your home, delete this email.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Trust me, once you hear what just happened to my clients‚Äô home, you might seriously consider selling‚Äîeven if you weren‚Äôt planning on it.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs the story:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">I just sold 44 Haven Street for $25,000 above the Zestimate, and here‚Äôs the kicker:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><ul id=""><li id="">We generated 63,000 views across social media</li><li id="">It had 8 private showings in 72 hours.</li><li id="">It received 4 offers, all above asking price.</li></ul><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">How did we do it? Targeted marketing, expert pricing, and positioning that generated serious buzz‚Äîand motivated buyers.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs what this means for you:</p><p id="">‚Äç<br>With so much demand and limited inventory, your home could be worth a lot more than you think.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Knowing your home‚Äôs value doesn‚Äôt mean you have to sell. If anything, it just gives you a clearer financial picture, peace of mind, and more options down the road.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Even if you‚Äôre just a little curious, wouldn‚Äôt it be worth finding out for sure?</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Text me at 555-555-5555, and I‚Äôll prepare a detailed report on your home‚Äôs value (and yes, it‚Äôs free).</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">I look forward to hearing from you, <br>[Agent Name]</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">p.s. Here‚Äôs what our client had to say about the experience: [Insert Testimonial]</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/you-might-regret-reading-this/example-you-might-regret-reading-this.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', true, true);

