VALUES ('[Coming Soon] Don‚Äôt Say I Didn‚Äôt Warn You', 'coming-soon-dont-say-i-didnt-warn-you', '<p id="">Your listing marketing isn‚Äôt just about selling a home‚Äîit‚Äôs the best form of advertising you can do for your future sellers. </p><p id="">But too many agents see listing marketing as a task to check off, missing the bigger opportunity. Future sellers are watching closely. </p><p id="">They notice the creativity, care, and thought you put into promoting your clients‚Äô listings and think, "I want that for my home."</p><p id="">I challenge you to think differently about every aspect of your listing marketing.</p><p id="">Make it an irresistible showcase of your expertise, so every seller in your market says, "That‚Äôs the agent I need."</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/coming-soon-dont-say-i-didnt-warn-you/thumbnail-coming-soon-dont-say-i-didnt-warn-you.png', '<p>Don‚Äôt Say I Didn‚Äôt Warn You</p>', '<p id="">If you‚Äôre in your forever home, stop reading and delete this email.</p><p id=""> <br><br>Trust me‚Äîonce you see what I‚Äôm about to share, you won‚Äôt be able to unsee it.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">You‚Äôll long for it.<br>You‚Äôll dream about it.<br>It‚Äôll haunt you in the best way possible.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">You‚Äôre happy now. Stay happy. Hit delete.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">For the rest of you brave souls ready to take the risk...</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">The home I‚Äôm listing tomorrow is perfect. The location, the price, the design‚Äîit‚Äôs the full package. It‚Äôs so irresistible you‚Äôll want to call me <em id="">immediately</em> to schedule a private showing.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs the deal:</p><p id="">‚Äç<br>If you want a sneak peek before anyone else, <strong id="">send me a text at 555-555-555.</strong></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p>I look forward to hearing from you,</p><p>[Your Name]</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">P.S. Oh yeah‚Ä¶one more thing, I sent this email to 5,302 other potential buyers who are also reading this right now.</p>', NULL, 'Entire Database', ARRAY['past-clients', 'soi', 'direct-response'], NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Email/coming-soon-dont-say-i-didnt-warn-you/example-coming-soon-dont-say-i-didnt-warn-you.png', '[{"title":"Copy Subject Line and Message to CRM","body":""},{"title":"Transferring Email Content to CRM","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Copy Subject: Highlight and copy the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> from your email draft.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Subject: Open the email blast app and paste it into the <strong id=\"\">subject line</strong> field.</li><li id=\"\">Copy Email Content: Return to your draft, copy the <strong id=\"\">email content</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Paste Content: Paste it in the <strong id=\"\">message body</strong> of the email blast app.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Check for accuracy, then schedule or send the email.</li></ol><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', true, true);

