VALUES ('Deal of the Week Text', 'deal-of-the-week-text', '<p id="">The Deal of the Week strategy needs to be added to your weekly marketing SOPs.</p><p id="">It''s simple, repeatable, and highly effective.</p><p id="">‚Äç<a href="https://www.instagram.com/the.real.brad.mccallum/">Brad McCallum</a> sent a Deal of the Week email and got 20 replies.</p><p id="">But here''s the thing...&nbsp;</p><p id="">This email is just the beginning.</p><p id="">Repurpose your Deal of the Week into an IG poll and an SOI text.</p><p id="">This is how you can take a winning marketing campaign and maximize the impact.</p><p id="">Here''s the text. ‚¨áÔ∏è</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/deal-of-the-week-text/thumbnail-deal-of-the-week-text.png', 'text', 'Sphere of Influence', '<p>Hey [First Name],</p><p>Hope you''re well. I&nbsp;know that you''re not in the market right now, but I&nbsp;just came across a property in [area] that might be one of the very best deals on the market.</p><p>Here are the details:</p><p>- [feature 1]</p><p>- [feature 2]</p><p>- [feature 3]</p><p>- [feature 4]</p><p>Who do you know in your network that''s in the market and might be interested?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/deal-of-the-week-text/example-deal-of-the-week-text.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM.","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

