VALUES ('FSBO Text Script', 'fsbo-text-script', '<p id="">Most FSBO sellers screen calls from unknown numbers‚Äîespecially from agents. If they didn‚Äôt pick up, it‚Äôs not necessarily a ‚Äúno.‚Äù It just means they don‚Äôt know <em id="">why</em> they should talk to you yet.</p><p id="">This text is short, direct, and creates curiosity. Instead of sounding like another agent trying to ‚Äúwin the listing,‚Äù you‚Äôre positioning yourself as someone with genuine interest in their home. No sales pitch, just a reason for them to call you back.</p><p id="">The goal? Get them to engage. Once they respond, you can shift the conversation toward value‚Äîhelping them, not selling them.</p><p id="">Once you get them on the phone, use 1 of these 3 call scripts:<br>- <a href="http://listingleads.com/campaigns/fsbo-pricing-call-script" id="">FSBO&nbsp;Pricing Call Script</a><br>- <a href="http://listingleads.com/campaigns/fsbo-photos-call-script" id="">FSBO&nbsp;Photos Call Script<br></a>- <a href="http://listingleads.com/campaigns/fsbo-listing-description-call-script" id="">FSBO&nbsp;Listing Description Call Script</a></p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/fsbo-text-script/thumbnail-fsbo-text-script.png', 'text', 'Leads', '<p>Hi Tom,</p><p id=""><em id="">Hey, this is [Your Name] with [Your Brokerage]. I had a few questions about your property on Zillow at [Address]. Can you call me back when you have a moment?</em></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/fsbo-text-script/example-fsbo-text-script.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM.","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li>Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li>Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li>Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

