VALUES ('Goldilocks Strategy', 'goldilocks-strategy', '<p id="">This is the perfect conversation starter to send to your SOI.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id=""><a href="https://www.instagram.com/lisbethherrerarealtor/" id="">Lisbeth Herrera</a> initially created this campaign as an IG poll (you can check it out here).</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">The results?&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">11 people responded with "too small."</p><p id="">3 CMAs requested.</p><p id="">1 appointment.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">You should always double down on your winners.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This campaign is perfect for a text and/or DM.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Your SOI is in your competition''s database.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Act accordingly.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Let''s get to work. üöÄ</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/goldilocks-strategy/thumbnail-goldilocks-strategy.png', 'text', NULL, '<p id=""><em id="">Hey [Insert Client Name],</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">Could you finish this sentence for me?</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">My house is‚Ä¶</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">1. Too small.</em></p><p id=""><em id="">2. Too big.</em></p><p id=""><em id="">3. The perfect size.</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">I''m asking all my clients. üôÇ</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">Can''t wait to hear your answer!</em></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/goldilocks-strategy/example-goldilocks-strategy.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

