VALUES ('Have you been following the market lately?', 'have-you-been-following-the-market-lately', '<p id="">The Thoughtful Conversation Starter campaign uses personalized SMS to engage potential clients with genuine, relevant messages.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id=""><strong>Why It Works</strong><br><br>This campaign leverages personalization and relevance, making recipients feel valued and piquing their curiosity about market conditions. This approach boosts response rates and strengthens client relationships.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id=""><strong>Value for Your Sphere of Influence</strong><br><br>Sending this message keeps you top-of-mind with clients, demonstrating your attentiveness and market expertise. By engaging clients with timely information, you build trust and loyalty, leading to more successful transactions and referrals.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/have-you-been-following-the-market-lately/thumbnail-have-you-been-following-the-market-lately.png', 'text', NULL, '<p id="">Hey Tom,&nbsp;</p><p id="">I was doing some equity checks for clients and I thought of you.&nbsp;</p><p id="">I‚Äôm seeing a lot of movement in your area.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Have you been following the market lately? </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/have-you-been-following-the-market-lately/example-have-you-been-following-the-market-lately.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

