VALUES ('If I could find you an off-market cash buyer...', 'off-market', '<p id="">Chris Voss talks about a negotiation technique he calls an Accusation Audit. It''s an preemptive approach that defuses any negative thoughts the other side might be thinking by proactively addressing them.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">So for this strategy, by framing a hypothetical question with, "I know this is a bit of a crazy question," you create a safe space to have an open dialogue and explore with your prospect.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s the script you can copy/paste.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Send this to 5 of your clients in your database this afternoon.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/off-market/thumbnail-off-market.png', 'text', NULL, '<p>I&nbsp;know this is a bit of a crazy question.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>If I could find you an off-market cash buyer for your property, who is going to pay the price you want for it, would you consider selling?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>No showings.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Move when it''s convenient.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/off-market/example-off-market.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

