VALUES ('Ken Pozek''s Equity Update', 'ken-pozeks-equity-update', '<p id="">Proactively sending CMAs is a killer strategy.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It''s exactly what <a href="http://instagram.com/kenpozek">Ken Pozek</a> and his team did to generate $80,000 in commission.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s the data he shared:</p><ul id=""><li>30 CMAs&nbsp;</li><li>12 Appointments Booked</li><li>5 Listings (all closed)&nbsp;</li><li>6 Deals in total (1 doubled-ended)&nbsp;</li></ul><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s the exact script his team used when they reached out to their SOI with their CMA.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Imagine if you started executing 5 of these a week?</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/ken-pozeks-equity-update/thumbnail-ken-pozeks-equity-update.png', 'text', NULL, '<p>Hi [First Name],</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I&nbsp;just wanted to do a quick equity update for you. It looks like homes like yours are selling between [$-$], depending on finishing and amenities.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I''m not sure if you''ve had any thoughts of selling this year, but even if you don''t, I was curious to see where you''re at.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/ken-pozeks-equity-update/example-1-ken-pozeks-equity-update.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

