VALUES ('Lead Activation Text - What‚Äôs The One Thing?', 'whats-the-one-thing', '<p id="">Boo Maddox pulled me aside after wrapping up a morning training session with Sharran to let me know that this EXACT sales question is helping unlock great conversations with prospects. </p><p id="">You can post this on social media, use it in your sales conversations, or just text a client you‚Äôve lost touch with.</p><p id="">Forget LPMAMMA and try this instead ‚¨áÔ∏è</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/whats-the-one-thing/thumbnail-whats-the-one-thing.png', 'text', 'Leads', '<p id="">Hi (Insert Lead Name), </p><p id="">Out of curiosity ‚Äî </p><p id="">What‚Äôs the one thing your current home is missing that your next one must have?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/whats-the-one-thing/example-whats-the-one-thing.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM.","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li>Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li>Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li>Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

