VALUES ('Listing Appointment Script', 'listing-appointment-script', '<p id="">Don‚Äôt wait until you secure the listing to start building relationships with the neighbors.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs a technique to implement as soon as you book the listing appointment:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">1. Build a list of nearby homes using a tool like Propstream.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">2. Enrich the list with contact information (skip tracing).</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">3. Use the following script to make calls and send personalized emails.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If the first time the neighbors hear from you is when you‚Äôve sold the home, you‚Äôre missing valuable opportunities.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">By consistently engaging with neighbors at each stage of the listing process, you‚Äôre doing more than selling a home‚Äîyou‚Äôre building your listing pipeline.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This strategy can effectively transform one listing opportunity into two or three additional ones. </p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/listing-appointment-script/thumbnail-listing-appointment-script.png', 'text', NULL, '<p>Hi [First Name],</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>My name is [Your Name], I''m a real estate agent with [Your Team].</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I know you''re not expecting my call right now but the reason I''m reaching out is because I''m actually meeting with one of your neighbors on Tuesday at 1pm to discuss selling their home.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I''m calling around the neighborhood because I''m offering a free home equity update while I''m in the area to folks who are exploring the idea of selling.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I''m not sure if it''s for you but I''m happy to swing by after my appointment and provide some insight on how much you could get for your home in today''s market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Would that be something you''d be interested in?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/listing-appointment-script/example-listing-appointment-script.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

