VALUES ('Market Like You Gossip', 'market-like-you-gossip', '<p id="">Forget the hard sell. Instead, market like you gossip. Instead of laying out every detail, tease your audience with just enough insider information to spark curiosity.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Imagine texts that start with, "I probably shouldn‚Äôt be telling you this but‚Ä¶" and then hint at great deals or hidden opportunities. Research shows that curiosity-driven messaging can boost engagement significantly.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Challenge the norm‚Äîlet this campaign show you how a playful, coy approach can help you start more conversations.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><figure id="" class="w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-fullwidth" style="max-width:2324px" data-rt-type="image" data-rt-align="fullwidth" data-rt-max-width="2324px"><div id=""><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b3c5fd1ff8bd0fdc5ee861/67b8ce7dc663e6b974147663_1-%20Main%20Image%20To%20upload-1.png" loading="lazy" alt="__wf_reserved_inherit" width="auto" height="auto" id=""></div></figure>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/market-like-you-gossip/thumbnail-market-like-you-gossip.png', 'text', 'Prospects', '<p id="">Hi Tom, </p><p id="">I probably shouldn‚Äôt be telling you this but I just came across a 4-bed, 3-bath home on the market in Bedford that I think would take a much lower price. </p><p id="">Worth talking about?</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/market-like-you-gossip/example-market-like-you-gossip.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM.","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li>Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li>Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li>Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

