VALUES ('Market Update Text', 'totw-market-update', '<p id="">Whenever you have a <em id="">marketable moment</em>‚Äîlike a client receiving multiple offers, selling above their online estimate, or going under contract quickly‚Äîit‚Äôs the perfect time to send a 1-to-1 text like this.&nbsp;</p><p id="">The power of this message comes from <em id="">herd mentality</em>‚Äîwhen people see others having success in the market, they naturally start wondering if they should make a move too.&nbsp;</p><p id="">The phrase <em id="">‚ÄúHave you noticed what‚Äôs been going on in our market?‚Äù</em> is a soft, easy-to-answer question that invites conversation without pressure.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Customize the first line of this text based on what you‚Äôve helped your clients accomplish recently. Here are a few ideas:<br></p><figure id="" class="w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-fullwidth" style="max-width:2324px" data-rt-type="image" data-rt-align="fullwidth" data-rt-max-width="2324px"><div id=""><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b3c5fd1ff8bd0fdc5ee861/679c7e3b4e9c2e629fc9ac44_679c7e346e658672e63fc1b5_99-%2520Main%2520Image%2520To%2520upload.png" loading="lazy" alt="__wf_reserved_inherit" width="auto" height="auto" id=""></div></figure>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-market-update/thumbnail-totw-market-update.png', 'text', 'Prospects', '<p id="">Hi Tom,</p><p id=""> <br></p><p id="">Just had a client get 8 offers on their home last week.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">I shared this with a few of my clients and it''s causing them to rethink their timeline on selling.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Have you noticed what‚Äôs been going on in our market?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-market-update/example-1-totw-market-update.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM.","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li>Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li>Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li>Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

