VALUES ('One More Thing: Hidden Sellers', 'one-more-thing-hidden-sellers', '<p id="">One of the ways you can find hidden sellers is by using the right script when you call your buyer leads.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Now, when most agents call their buyer leads, they ask,<em id=""> "Do you have a home to sell?"</em> in hopes of getting the listing appointment.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">The problem? Most consumers will immediately put up a wall.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Because they''re contacting you to schedule a showing, to try to find a home‚Äîmost of them don''t want to talk about putting their home up for sale just yet.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">So here''s what to do instead:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Instead of asking that question at the <em id="">beginning</em> of the conversation, use the following script <em id="">after</em> you book the appointment.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">This simple swap will lead to significantly better results.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/one-more-thing-hidden-sellers/thumbnail-one-more-thing-hidden-sellers.png', 'text', NULL, '<p>One more thing‚Äîas part of the client experience, we''re going to prepare you a home value report so that you can understand what your buying power is in today''s market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>When is the last time you''ve had a professional home value report prepared?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/one-more-thing-hidden-sellers/example-one-more-thing-hidden-sellers.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

