VALUES ('One More Thing: Referral Script', 'one-more-thing-referral-script', '<p id="">Asking for referrals can feel hard.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This script reframes the typical referral script.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">The phrase "One more thing" are magic words that you can slide into the end of a conversation with your client.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">From there, make a genuine offer to help someone in their network.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Try it out. ‚¨áÔ∏è</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/one-more-thing-referral-script/thumbnail-one-more-thing-referral-script.png', 'text', NULL, '<p>One more thing‚Äîwe''ve been talking to a lot of folks who are really struggling in this market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Can you think of anyone in your network who hasn''t been able to buy or sell that you think we can help?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/one-more-thing-referral-script/example-one-more-thing-referral-script.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

