VALUES ('SOI Mortgage Rate Alert', 'soi-mortgage-rate-alert', '<p>The #1 reason why won‚Äôt of your client won‚Äôt sell their current home is because they have a great interest rate. As rates drop, they become more open to the idea of making a move. Let‚Äôs take this opportunity to engage our SOI to find our next listing.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/soi-mortgage-rate-alert/thumbnail-soi-mortgage-rate-alert.png', 'text', 'SOI', '<p id="">Hi (CLIENT NAME),</p><p id="">I wanted to make sure you saw the news.</p><p id="">Last week, mortgage rates dropped from 7% to the low-mid 6‚Äôs in just 48 hours.</p><p id="">That‚Äôs a $300-$400/month savings on an $800,000 loan.</p><p id="">Would you like me to keep you in the loop if they drop any lower?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/soi-mortgage-rate-alert/example-soi-mortgage-rate-alert.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

