VALUES ('SOI Text', 'soi-text', '<p id="">This SOI (Sphere of Influence) message utilizes Chris Voss''s acquisition audit technique.<br>‚Äç</p><p id="">The aim is straightforward: remove any pressure from the conversation and gently uncover your client''s plans without being pushy or aggressive.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/soi-text/thumbnail-soi-text.png', 'text', '10-20 Clients', '<p id="">I know selling your home might feel like a hassle, especially with everything going on. </p><p id="">You‚Äôre probably not even thinking about it.</p><p id="">But I have to ask‚Ä¶ if you got a great offer, would you consider it?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/soi-text/example-soi-text.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

