VALUES ('Seller Script for Building Your Listing Pipeline', 'seller-script-for-building-your-listing-pipeline', '<p id="">Almost everyone has a prediction on where they think the market is headed.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">And it''s a really interesting angle for engaging 1-to-1 with your SOI: <em id="">What do they think is going to happen with the market?</em></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This 3-part text script is an opportunity to find people who are thinking about selling, but who haven''t yet raised their hand.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s how to start the conversation. ‚¨áÔ∏è</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/seller-script-for-building-your-listing-pipeline/thumbnail-seller-script-for-building-your-listing-pipeline.png', 'text', NULL, '<p>Hey [First Name], I have a quick favor to ask.</p>', '<p>I''m conducting a research project and I wanted to get your opinion. Do you feel that your home''s value is going to increase over the next 12 months?</p>', '<p>Thank you so much for that. Super helpful. One more thing...Just out of curiosity, what would need to happen for you to want to sell your home this year?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/seller-script-for-building-your-listing-pipeline/example-seller-script-for-building-your-listing-pipeline.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li>