VALUES ('Spring Planning Text', 'spring-planning-text', '<p id="">The spring market might be the best time of year to touch base with your past clients.</p><p id="">This simple text not only allows you to nurture these relationships, it also positions you as a proactive advisor in their real estate plans.</p><p id="">Tap into the spring momentum with this "Spring Planning Text"‚Äîand use it as a way to start more conversations.</p><p id="">Don''t overthink it‚Äîsend this text today. üëá</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/spring-planning-text/thumbnail-spring-planning-text.png', 'text', NULL, '<p id="">Hey [Insert Client Name],</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">We‚Äôre seeing a wave of new homes hit the market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Thought I‚Äôd check back with you before the spring season starts.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Any real estate plans you think I should know about?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/spring-planning-text/example-spring-planning-text.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

