VALUES ('TMA', 'tma-canada', '<p id="">Way too many agents are waiting for people to raise their hand to say they want to sell.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">As a result, they''re not getting the opportunities they''re looking for and they''re not hitting the goals they want to hit.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">The TMA strategy is so incredibly simple.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Every day, 2-3 times a day, choose someone from your database or someone in your SOI, take a screenshot of their home value on Properly, HouseSigma, or Ownerly, and send this exact text message.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">That''s it.‚Äç</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you do 2-3 of these every day, that will turn into 2-3 conversations per day, which will likely lead to 1-2 listing appointments a week, which will likely lead to 2-3 listings a month.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">That math just works.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This has got to be in your daily SOP.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/tma-canada/thumbnail-tma-canada.png', 'text', NULL, '<p>Hi [First Name]</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I&nbsp;was online earlier today looking for a few properties in your neighbourhood, and I&nbsp;thought I''d check out your home''s value. They estimate your home''s value is [$].</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>[INSERT SCREENSHOT]</p>', '<p>I&nbsp;have my opinion, but I''d love to hear your thoughts.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>What do you think?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/tma-canada/example-tma-canada.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'CA', false, true);

