VALUES ('TOTW: Annual Check-Up', 'totw-annual-checkup', '<p id="">By framing the question around a number that would make them feel ‚Äúcrazy not to sell,‚Äù you‚Äôre leveraging the concept of <em id="">loss aversion</em>. It subtly encourages the homeowner to consider what they could gain by selling and what they might miss out on if they don‚Äôt. This message invites homeowners to think about their home''s value in a low-pressure, conversational way‚Äîmaking it easier for them to engage with you.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-annual-checkup/thumbnail-totw-annual-checkup.png', 'text', '10-20 Clients', '<p id="">Hi Tom,&nbsp;</p><p id="">You know I have to ask this at least once a year‚Ä¶.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Is there a number you have in mind that would be ‚ÄúI‚Äôd be crazy not to sell?‚Äù</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-annual-checkup/example-totw-annual-checkup.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

