VALUES ('TOTW: Bad Timing Text', 'totw-bad-timing-text', '<p id="">Most agents think prospecting is about persistence‚Äîjust make more calls, send more texts, and eventually, something will stick. But volume isn‚Äôt the problem. <strong id="">Relevance is.</strong></p><p id="">The truth? Consumers aren‚Äôt ignoring you because they don‚Äôt want to sell. They‚Äôre hesitating because of the voice in their head:</p><ul id=""><li><em id="">Interest rates are still high.</em></li><li><em id="">The stock market is correcting.</em></li><li><em id="">The economy feels uncertain.</em></li><li><em id="">What if prices drop?</em></li></ul><p id="">If you don‚Äôt address that voice, you‚Äôll lose them before the conversation even starts.</p><p id="">That‚Äôs why this text works. It flips the script‚Äîacknowledging their hesitation up front, instead of pretending it doesn‚Äôt exist. It disarms, engages, and clears the path for real conversations.</p><p id="">It‚Äôs a simple shift, but it changes everything.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-bad-timing-text/thumbnail-totw-bad-timing-text.png', 'text', 'Cold Leads', '<p id="">Hi (Insert Name),&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">I know this is probably the wrong time but I‚Äôve been talking to a lot of buyers who are <strong id="">very serious</strong> about buying in the next 90 days. </p><p id="">‚Äç<br></p><p id="">Would you be open to the idea of selling if you got a great offer?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-bad-timing-text/example-totw-bad-timing-text.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM.","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

