VALUES ('TOTW: Gratitude Text', 'totw-gratitude-text', '<p>Gratitude isn‚Äôt just a feel-good sentiment; it‚Äôs a powerful psychological tool. When you express genuine appreciation, it activates positive emotions in your clients, strengthening trust and deepening relationships. Studies show that gratitude fosters reciprocity‚Äîclients are more likely to stay loyal, refer others, and feel good about their decision to work with you. It‚Äôs a small gesture with a big impact on both personal and professional connections.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-gratitude-text/thumbnail-totw-gratitude-text.png', 'text', 'Text this to 50 of your closest clients.', '<p id="">As we reflect on this year, I just wanted to take a moment to say thank you. </p><p id="">Your trust and support mean the world to me, and I‚Äôm truly grateful for the opportunity to help you with your real estate journey. </p><p id="">Wishing you and your loved ones a wonderful season ahead!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-gratitude-text/example-totw-gratitude-text.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

