VALUES ('TOTW: Interest Rates Buydown', 'interest-rates-buydown', '<p id=""><strong id="">What‚Äôs stopping your prospective clients from making a move? High-interest rates?</strong></p><p id="">For many, it‚Äôs the <em id="">only</em> thing holding them back.</p><p id="">In fact, sellers are seven times more likely to list their home in a 5% interest rate environment compared to 6%.</p><p id="">That‚Äôs why this script is so effective.</p><p id="">Text it to 50 of your cold prospects (buyers and sellers) today and see the difference.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/interest-rates-buydown/thumbnail-interest-rates-buydown.png', 'text', 'Leads', '<p id="">Hi (Insert Name)&nbsp;</p><p id="">I just helped my client get a 5.75% interest rate on their home. <br><br>This was surprising to a lot of their friends.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Has anyone sat down to walk you through how a mortgage buydown works?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/interest-rates-buydown/example-interest-rates-buydown.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM.","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li>Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li>Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li>Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

