VALUES ('TOTW: Post-Election Text', 'totw-post-election-text', '<p id="">This text was sent to 75 people, started 10 conversations and generated 2 appointments (1 listening and 1 buyer consultation)&nbsp;</p><p id="">Now that the US presidential election is over, it‚Äôs time to reconnect and check in with all those clients and prospects who have been holding off on making a move.&nbsp;</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-post-election-text/thumbnail-totw-post-election-text.png', 'text', 'Leads', '<p id="">Hi Tom,</p><p id="">A lot of my clients have been holding off on their real estate plans until after the election.</p><p id="">Now that it‚Äôs over, I wanted to reach back out to you to see if it would be helpful to discuss your real estate plans.</p><p id="">Looking forward to hearing from you!</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/totw-post-election-text/example-totw-post-election-text.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

