VALUES ('The Matchmaker Strategy', 'the-matchmaker-strategy', '<p id="">This is a tactic we like to call The Matchmaker Strategy.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s how it works:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">1. After you sell a property, call your buyer leads using the first script.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">2. Then, after you call your buyer leads, call homeowners in the area using the next script.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It''s that simple.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Try it and see if it works for you.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/the-matchmaker-strategy/thumbnail-the-matchmaker-strategy.png', 'text', NULL, '<p>Hey [First Name],</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>This is [Your Name] calling with [Your Team]. The reason I''m reaching out is because we just sold 123 Main Street.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I''m going to be calling around the neighborhood to see if anyone is interested in putting their house on the market.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>If I come across any deals, would you like me to keep you in the loop?</p>', '<p>Hey [First Name],</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>This is [Your Name] calling with [Your Team]. The reason I''m reaching out is because I actually just spoke to a buyer who''s thinking about making a move. They''re interested in homes in your area.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>I''m not sure if this is for you, but out of curiosity‚Äîhave you had any thoughts about putting your home on the market?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/the-matchmaker-strategy/example-the-matchmaker-strategy.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

