VALUES ('Unsolicited CMA: Comparison Text (US)', 'unsolicited-cma-comparison-text-us', '<p id="">Most agents play the long game with home value leads, waiting months‚Äîsometimes years‚Äîfor them to convert. But if you want to <em id="">fill your listing pipeline now</em>, you need to focus on a different group: homeowners requesting CMAs.</p><p id="">Why? Because <strong id="">18% of homeowners who request a CMA list their home within 12 months</strong>. (Source: Fello) That‚Äôs nearly 1 in 5. And while most agents chase colder leads, this strategy puts you in front of sellers who are already thinking about making a move.</p><p id="">This text is so effective because it <em id="">challenges assumptions</em>. Homeowners trust online estimates, but when they see how far off they can be, it sparks curiosity‚Äîand that curiosity turns into conversation.</p><p id="">Send this text to 25 people in your SOI today. The opportunities are out there. You just have to start the right conversation.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/unsolicited-cma-comparison-text-us/thumbnail-unsolicited-cma-comparison-text-us.png', 'text', 'Prospects', '<p id="">Hi Sandra,</p><p id="">I just finished a home value report for a client, and I think you‚Äôll find this interesting‚Ä¶</p><p id="">Zillow valued their home at $692,000.</p><p id="">Redfin said $743,000.</p><p id="">Realtor.com estimated $702,000.</p><p id="">But here‚Äôs the kicker‚Äîthe actual value is between $810,000-$850,000.</p><p id="">Can I prepare one for your home?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/unsolicited-cma-comparison-text-us/example-unsolicited-cma-comparison-text-us.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM.","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li>Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li>Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li>Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

