VALUES ('Unsolicited CMA: Home Improvement', 'unsolicited-cma-home-improvement', '<p id="">Most agents wait for homeowners to <em id="">ask</em> about their home‚Äôs value. But the best agents don‚Äôt wait for permission to be helpful. They anticipate the need and show up with value‚Äî<em id="">before</em> the homeowner even thinks to ask.</p><p id="">That‚Äôs what makes this text so effective. Instead of offering a generic CMA, you‚Äôre telling them you‚Äôre already working on it. It‚Äôs proactive, it‚Äôs personal, and it naturally sparks a conversation.</p><p id="">This text campaign is simple but powerful. Instead of just handing over a home value report, it starts a conversation. By asking about recent or planned updates, you engage the homeowner, make them think differently about their investment, and position yourself as the expert who helps them maximize it.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/unsolicited-cma-home-improvement/thumbnail-unsolicited-cma-home-improvement.png', 'text', 'SOI', '<p id="">Hi Tom,</p><p id="">I‚Äôm preparing an updated home value report for you.</p><p id="">Before I send it over, have you made any updates to your home recently or are you planning any home improvement projects in the next few months?</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/unsolicited-cma-home-improvement/example-unsolicited-cma-home-improvement.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM.","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li>Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li>Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li>Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li>Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

