VALUES ('Value Based Voicemail: Just Sold Strategy', 'value-based-voicemail-just-sold-strategy', '<p id="">Every time you sell a home, it''s an opportunity to circle prospect around the neighborhood and execute what we call the Value-Based Voicemail strategy.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">The strategy is simple‚Äî</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">1. Give them valuable information about the sale that they might not find online.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">2. Ask them if they know of anyone who''s thinking about selling, to have them give you a call.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This exact script landed <a href="https://www.instagram.com/conniecarlson/">Connie Carlson </a><em id="">another</em> listing opportunity just after she sold her listing $40K over the asking price.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/value-based-voicemail-just-sold-strategy/thumbnail-value-based-voicemail-just-sold-strategy.png', 'text', NULL, '<p id="">Hi, this is [Your Name] with [Your Team]. The reason I''m reaching out is because we recently sold your neighbor''s home at 123 Main Street. They actually closed on Thursday and got $40K&nbsp;over asking.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Typically when something like this happens, a few people in the neighborhood start to think about moving. So if you know of anyone who might be interested in selling, call me back at 555-555-5555.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">I look forward to hearing from you.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/value-based-voicemail-just-sold-strategy/example-value-based-voicemail-just-sold-strategy.png', '[{"title":"Copy the message content and send it via SMS or DM","body":""},{"title":"Sending Your Message via Mass SMS or DM Tool","body":"<ol id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Log In to Your Mass Messaging Tool: Open your mass SMS or DM platform and log in to your account. (or simply use your phone)</li><li id=\"\">Select or Upload Recipients: Choose your audience (contacts/followers) or selecting recipients within the tool.</li><li id=\"\">Compose the Message: Paste the copied message content into the message field.</li><li id=\"\">Review and Send: Double-check the message for accuracy, then hit \"Send\" to distribute to all selected recipients.</li></ol>"}]', 'US', false, true);

