VALUES ('Zillow Vs. Agent Call Script', 'zillow-vs-agent-call-script', '<p id="">Anytime a home sells, 2 or 3 people start thinking about making a move. There is no better opportunity to book a listing appointment than after a recent sale. This campaign requires a bit more legwork but will pay dividends.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Step 1:</strong> Analyze recent sales in your desired farm area.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Step 2:</strong> Identify notable sales that sold quickly and for a premium.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Step 3:</strong> Visit the home''s Zillow page to see if their Zestimate was much lower than their actual sales price. You can do this by clicking on the Zestimate history.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Step 4:</strong> Build a call list of the closest 100 homes near that notable sale, using your title rep or PropStream.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Step 5:</strong> Print the list of prospective homeowners. On your call sheet, add a section for their Zestimate. Fill in their Zestimate and begin calling using this script:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/zillow-vs-agent-call-script/thumbnail-zillow-vs-agent-call-script.png', 'text', '250-500 homes near the recent sale (ideally owned the home for 7+ years with 50% equity', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Text%20&%20Voice/zillow-vs-agent-call-script/example-zillow-vs-agent-call-script.png', NULL, 'US', false, true);

