VALUES ('Better Than An iBuyer', 'better-than-an-ibuyer', '<p id="">This stat blew me away: Opendoor has purchased 30,000 homes over the last two years.</p><p id="">Now, why does this matter? As an agent who wants more listings, you need to identify underserved niches in the market and get the right message in front of them.&nbsp;</p><p id="">When I look at Reddit and other forums, sellers who choose Opendoor often mention convenience, certainty, and speed‚Äîbut overwhelmingly, the biggest reason is <em id="">avoiding repairs.</em> They don‚Äôt want the hassle of fixing up their home before selling.</p><p id="">That‚Äôs a huge opportunity. Homeowners who have lived in their homes for 20+ years likely have repairs to make, and many believe their only option is selling to an iBuyer. This direct mail campaign speaks <em id="">directly</em> to them, showing a better alternative‚Äî<strong id="">you</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Use this letter to stop losing deals to companies like Opendoor and position yourself as the agent who knows how to get their home sold.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/better-than-an-ibuyer/thumbnail-better-than-an-ibuyer.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGdsj0msq0/ZgyIxQfQmvuzAnN6Otk8sQ/view?utm_content=DAGdsj0msq0&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, 'Farm', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/better-than-an-ibuyer/example-better-than-an-ibuyer.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:<ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul></li><li><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</strong>: Submit the flattened PDF file to your print shop for printing.</li>"}]', 'US', false, true);

