VALUES ('Better Than An iBuyer (Home Improvements)', 'better-than-an-ibuyer-home-improvements', '<p id="">Most sellers assume that making updates before listing is a <em id="">must</em>. But the truth? Some renovations add value‚Äîothers just drain your wallet.</p><p id="">This <strong id="">direct mail sales letter</strong> challenges the idea that every home needs a facelift before hitting the market. Instead of pushing sellers toward costly upgrades, it positions you as a strategic advisor‚Äîsomeone who helps them make <em id="">smart</em> decisions based on real market data. The message is clear: before they waste time and money on unnecessary projects, they should talk to you first.</p><p id="">To make this even more compelling, the letter includes a <strong id="">visual graphic</strong> highlighting specific home improvements and their return on investment. This gives sellers a quick, digestible way to see which updates <em id="">actually</em> pay off.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Pro tip:</strong> Update the ROI data based on your local market insights. Customizing these numbers will make the letter even more relevant and persuasive for homeowners in your area.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/better-than-an-ibuyer-home-improvements/thumbnail-better-than-an-ibuyer-home-improvements.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGecKoNIKs/B2SmSZ9zv36YVSRNVdYvzA/view?utm_content=DAGecKoNIKs&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, 'Farm', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/better-than-an-ibuyer-home-improvements/example-better-than-an-ibuyer-home-improvements.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>