VALUES ('Charlie King Magic Buyer Letter', 'charlie-king-magic-buyer-letter', '<p id="">You might already be familiar with the Magic Buyer strategy‚Äîa direct mail strategy that engages potential sellers by outlining who your buyers are and what they''re looking for.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This is the <a href="https://www.instagram.com/the_charles_king_group/" id="">Charlie King</a> version.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Within 1 week, Charlie King had 5 calls from this letter.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">S/O to <a href="https://www.instagram.com/applebaum.kc.homes/" id="">Jeremy Applebaum</a> who <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5qbYiyu_NJ/" id="">sent out 83 Magic Buyer Letters</a> and landed 3 appointments.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It''s simple:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">1. Write a letter to homeowners who live in the neighborhood where your buyer is looking to live.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">2. Provide context on the situation and be specific in describing what your buyers bring to the table.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">3. Include a direct response CTA if they''re interested in selling.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">By directly engaging homeowners with specific details about what the buyer is looking for‚Äîand showcasing the serious intent of your clients‚Äîyou not only pique interest but also position yourself as a proactive, dedicated agent.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Below you''ll find two examples of this letter‚Äîthe first is Charlie King''s original. The second is my version.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Let''s get to work.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/charlie-king-magic-buyer-letter/thumbnail-charlie-king-magic-buyer-letter.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGCaCkAVQY/s4DtnAhD_z6mvh8GDRs4bg/view?utm_content=DAGCaCkAVQY&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/charlie-king-magic-buyer-letter/example-charlie-king-magic-buyer-letter.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:</p><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</strong>: Submit the flattened PDF file to your print shop for printing.</li><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

