VALUES ('Compare Options: The Anti-Gimmick Approach', 'anti-gimmick', '<p id="">Words can develop a reputation.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">And the "Cash Offer" has been abused.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">We all know that it can be a viable option for a specific type of consumer, but it can feel predatory when it''s pitched a certain way.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">So, we''ve developed a new campaign.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">It''s the anti-gimmick approach.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s why it works:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">1. The front of the card grabs attention</p><p id="">2. The language takes the pressure off the consumer and puts you on the same side of the table</p><p id="">3. It includes social proof to prove that you''re great at your job</p><p id="">4. It ends with a direct response CTA</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">See what you think. üëá</p><p id="">‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/anti-gimmick/thumbnail-anti-gimmick.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAF_liTRieY/877OcWMPRdWF8ia2bD59Xw/view?utm_content=DAF_liTRieY&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', 'https://app.listingleads.com/postcard-editor/538ca86d-838f-419e-8608-57b115ce5fe2', NULL, 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/anti-gimmick/example-anti-gimmick.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:</p><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for