VALUES ('Comparison postcard', 'comparison-postcard', '<p id="">By contrasting the outdated, passive approach of "homes that sit" with the proactive, high-impact strategies of "homes that sell," we don''t just highlight the services we offer‚Äîwe show sellers that their home deserves the best. We validate their desire for a successful sale by providing proof that with the right approach, they can achieve a higher sale price, faster.</p><p id="">‚Äç<br>This messaging isn''t just about listing features; it''s about instilling confidence. It reassures sellers that by choosing your company, they are making a smart, informed decision that will lead to tangible benefits: more equity in their pockets and a smoother, faster sale process.</p><p>‚Äç</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/comparison-postcard/thumbnail-comparison-postcard.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGONinziB4/2jKaffb-0hFuACbUyg9HfA/view?utm_content=DAGONinziB4&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, '1000 Homeowners with 7+ years ownership + 50% equity', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/comparison-postcard/example-comparison-postcard.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:</p><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\