VALUES ('Days On Market Emoji Postcard', 'days-on-market-emoji-postcard', '<p id="">S/O to Jeremy Davis from <a href="https://palmagent.com/" id="">Palm Agent</a>.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you haven''t downloaded their app, they have a killer feature that allows you to calculate the holding cost based on the sales price.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If a home is on the market for 30 days, 60 days, 90 days, 120 days‚Äîhow much does it <em id="">actually</em> cost the consumer to have their property sit on the market?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Let''s say, for example, that a $725,000 home is on the market for 90 days. The holding costs could be upwards of $19,000-20,000.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Most sellers wouldn''t know that. In their mind, what''s the big deal if it''s 7 days or 45 days?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">It matters because it could literally cost them thousands of dollars in equity they''ve earned.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This campaign is a great opportunity for you to communicate why your ability to sell a home quickly actually matters to the consumer.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Plus, it''ll stand out in the mailbox.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/days-on-market-emoji-postcard/thumbnail-days-on-market-emoji-postcard.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAF_J2fo5Zc/BbCK57PrucC8tfjP5UrVAw/view?utm_content=DAF_J2fo5Zc&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', 'https://app.listingleads.com/postcard-editor/426c930b-0107-486e-86c8-aa12f340465d', NULL, 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/days-on-market-emoji-postcard/example-days-on-market-emoji-postcard.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:</p><ul id=\"\"><