VALUES ('FSBO Letter #1: 3 Tips', 'fsbo-letter-1-3-tips', '<p id="">Most FSBO sellers expect agents to pressure them into listing. That‚Äôs why most direct mail from agents goes straight into the trash.</p><p id="">If you want to stand out, you have to do something different. Instead of pushing for a listing, this letter builds trust by meeting sellers where they are‚Äîacknowledging their frustrations, offering value, and positioning you as a helpful resource, not just another agent looking for a deal.</p><p id="">This is letter #1 in a three-part sequence. The goal? To shift their perception of you from ‚Äújust another agent‚Äù to someone they can actually trust. No sales pitch, no scare tactics‚Äîjust practical advice that makes them feel more confident in their sale.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/fsbo-letter-1-3-tips/thumbnail-fsbo-letter-1-3-tips.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGgZzUhjpQ/rUpzyX-Ur6mDVmw48KKh2Q/view?utm_content=DAGgZzUhjpQ&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, 'FSBO Sellers', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/fsbo-letter-1-3-tips/example-fsbo-letter-1-3-tips.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:<ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul></li><li><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</stron