VALUES ('FSBO Letter #2: CMA Offer', 'fsbo-letter-2-cma-offer', '<p id="">By now, the FSBO seller has likely dealt with lowball offers, pushy agents, or worse‚Äîradio silence. And if their home isn‚Äôt moving, they‚Äôre starting to wonder why.</p><p id="">That‚Äôs where this letter comes in. Letter #2 in the sequence shifts the conversation to pricing‚Äîone of the biggest pain points for FSBO sellers. Instead of telling them they‚Äôve priced it wrong, this letter leads with empathy, highlights the risk of guessing, and offers a free CMA as a straightforward, no-pressure solution.</p><p id="">The goal? To make it easy for them to say yes. No obligation, no catch‚Äîjust valuable data that helps them make smarter decisions. And when they realize they need more than just numbers? You‚Äôre already the agent they trust.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/fsbo-letter-2-cma-offer/thumbnail-fsbo-letter-2-cma-offer.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGgZ-qDV7w/2hhifMTR5sRaQWcgo5hwig/view?utm_content=DAGgZ-qDV7w&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, 'FSBO Sellers', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/fsbo-letter-2-cma-offer/example-fsbo-letter-2-cma-offer.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:<ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul></li><li><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</strong>: Submit the flattened PDF file to your print shop for printing.</li>"}]', 'US', false, true);

