VALUES ('Jason Wright Name Your Price Direct Mail', 'jason-wright-name-your-price', '<p id=""><a href="https://www.instagram.com/jasonwrightocre/?hl=en" id="">Jason Wright</a> brilliantly executed the Name Your Price direct mail campaign.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">The results?</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">5000 sends. 500+ QR code scans. <strong id="">8+ listing appointments.</strong></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">And here''s the thing‚Äîhe <em id="">only</em> included a QR code. That''s it. (see the example below)</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">The QR code drove traffic to <a href="https://www.timsmithrealestategroup.com/whats-your-price-to-sell-jason-wright" id="">a custom landing page</a> where the consumer answers 3 quick questions:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">1. The price they''d want to list for</p><p id="">2. Their property address</p><p id="">3. Their email and contact info</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id=""><em id="">(He did this via a typeform survey on the landing page that integrates into Follow Up Boss)</em></p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Then he followed up immediately.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Marketing‚Äîdone like this‚Äîis magic. üî•</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">To create your own QR&nbsp;code, simply build your landing page, add the URL to the Canva template below, and download your design as PDF&nbsp;Print. Watch this video to see exactly how to do it. üëá</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><div data-rt-embed-type=''true''><div style="padding:62.5% 0 0 0;position:relative;"><iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/922733634?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;" title="How to Add A QR Code to Your Canva Template"></iframe></div><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></div>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/jason-wright-name-your-price/thumbnail-jason-wright-name-your-price.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAF_MOYmfSw/AbBbNDyUUXkQpkqphFEohw/view?utm_content=DAF_MOYmfSw&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/jason-wright-name-your-price/example-jason-wright-name-your-price.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:</p><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</strong>: Submit the flattened PDF file to your print shop for printing.</li><p>‚Äç</p>"}]', 'US', false, true);

