VALUES ('Just Listed Letter', 'just-listed-letter', '<p id="">A <em id="">Just Listed</em> letter isn‚Äôt just about announcing a new listing‚Äîit‚Äôs about making homeowners pay attention to how it could impact <em id="">their</em> home‚Äôs value. Every sale in a neighborhood sets a new benchmark, influencing what buyers are willing to pay. This letter shifts the conversation from <em id="">‚ÄúOh, another home for sale‚Äù</em> to <em id="">‚ÄúWhy should I care?‚Äù</em></p><p id="">It also serves another purpose: showcasing your marketing strategy without saying <em id="">‚ÄúLook how great I am.‚Äù</em> By sharing real numbers‚Äîsocial media views, private showings, buyer interest‚Äîyou‚Äôre proving that your approach gets results. And by offering to personally share the final sale details, you create an easy, value-driven way to stay in touch with potential future sellers.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Use this letter to position yourself as the agent who understands the market, drives demand, and keeps homeowners informed.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/just-listed-letter/thumbnail-just-listed-letter.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGeFN980W4/PUV57-FP7AGxqe5zmcj5JQ/view?utm_content=DAGeFN980W4&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, 'Radius List', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/just-listed-letter/example-just-listed-letter.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:<ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul></li><li><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</strong>: Submit the flattened PDF file to your print shop for printing.</li>"}]', 'US', false, true);

