VALUES ('Just Sold', 'just-sold', '<p id="">Just Sold Letters + Circle Dialing works.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">The following campaigns resulted in multiple listing appointments.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s the pro-tip:</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">1. Build a targeted list. Ideally, homes that fit in your local "sell-box."</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">2. Create a campaign that provides information the consumer can''t find online (i.e. # of offers, # of showings, etc.) with a simple and clear call-to-action. Don''t include the final sale price‚Äîthat gives potential sellers a reason to call.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">3. Make your offer clear and compelling.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">And finally, don''t wait for the inbound calls.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Hit the phones to follow up.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This needs to become an SOP every time you sell a home.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/just-sold/thumbnail-just-sold.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAF9IqwOf20/MqNqRbv3iiGZVb9zmG3eJw/view?utm_content=DAF9IqwOf20&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/just-sold/example-1-just-sold.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/just-sold/example-2-just-sold.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/just-sold/example-3-just-sold.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:</p><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</strong>: Submit the flattened PDF file to your print shop for printing.</li>"}]', 'US', false, true);

