VALUES ('Just Sold 2025', 'just-sold-2025', '<p id="">If you want to grab attention and convert curiosity into action, this campaign is your blueprint.</p><p id="">It‚Äôs built around three powerful marketing tactics designed to engage and persuade: Small Agreements, Objection Handling, and the Power of a Client Case Study.</p><p id="">By inviting homeowners to take a simple, no-pressure step‚Äîlike texting for a free home value report‚Äîit lowers barriers, builds trust, and encourages incremental commitment.</p><p id="">At the same time, it proactively addresses a common objection: ‚ÄúI don‚Äôt want to sell my home,‚Äù reframing the conversation to focus on clarity and future possibilities.</p><p id="">Including a real client success story‚Äîselling a home for $25,000 over Zestimate‚Äîadds credibility and proves your expertise, making your offer even more compelling.</p><p id="">Together, these strategies create a message that inspires action and helps you win your next listing.</p><p id="">Pro-Tip: Add your client‚Äôs testimonial in the P.S. to build even more credibility and trust.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/just-sold-2025/thumbnail-just-sold-2025.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGcGNuEi2w/LDslpGbXO56LkjBjeKOK7g/view?utm_content=DAGcGNuEi2w&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, 'Farm', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/just-sold-2025/example-just-sold-2025.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:<ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul></li><li><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</strong>: Submit the flattened PDF file to your print shop for printing.</li>"}]', 'US', false, true);

