VALUES ('ListingLeads.com‚Ä®Marketing Checklist', 'listingleads-com-marketing-checklist', '<p id="">As the year winds down, it‚Äôs the perfect time to pause, reflect, and get ready for what‚Äôs next. To make the most of this quieter season, we‚Äôve created the <strong id="">ListingLeads.com End-of-Year Marketing Checklist</strong>‚Äîa simple and effective way to fine-tune your brand and set yourself up for success in the New Year.</p><p id="">This checklist is your go-to guide for tackling those tasks that often get overlooked during busier months, such as:</p><ul id=""><li id="">Fixing broken links.</li><li id="">Updating your bios.</li><li id="">Cleaning up your database.</li></ul><p id="">‚Ä¶and more!</p><p id="">In just a few focused hours, you can complete these steps and enter 2025 with your brand in top shape. While others scramble to catch up, you‚Äôll already be ahead of the game‚Äîarmed with a solid plan to make this your best year yet.</p><p id="">So, take a moment to get started. You‚Äôll be glad you did when the New Year rolls around.</p><p id="">Enjoy the holidays! We‚Äôre excited to help you hit the ground running when we‚Äôre back on January 2nd.</p><p id=""><strong id="">Let‚Äôs make 2025 amazing together!</strong></p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/listingleads-com-marketing-checklist/thumbnail-listingleads-com-marketing-checklist.png', 'postcard', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1kDMusvOYPUUQ_ZW1BNMEpwbVr3AsyuaN/view?usp=sharing', NULL, 'Farm', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/listingleads-com-marketing-checklist/example-1-listingleads-com-marketing-checklist.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/listingleads-com-marketing-checklist/example-2-listingleads-com-marketing-checklist.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/listingleads-com-marketing-checklist/example-3-listingleads-com-marketing-checklist.png',