VALUES ('The Yellow Letter Strategy: Just Sold', 'the-yellow-letter-strategy-just-sold', '<p id="">This direct mail campaign generated a $2M listing.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Total spend, $1,200.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">We targeted 1,000 neighbors who had owned their homes for more than three years and had a property value of over $1.5M.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs why it worked:</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">1. We had social proof (‚ÄúYour neighbor hired us‚Äù).</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">2. We provided specifics about the sale that couldn‚Äôt be found online.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">3. We shared a relevant statistic that piqued their curiosity.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Most importantly, we had a clear and direct call to action targeted towards serious sellers.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">Bonus: We used <a href="https://www.yellowletterscomplete.com/" id="">Yellow Letters Complete</a> to create this campaign. They handwrite the notes using a robot, and you can add a custom sticky note that we find to be extremely effective in eliciting responses.</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><p id="">The cost is about $1.20 per piece.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/the-yellow-letter-strategy-just-sold/thumbnail-the-yellow-letter-strategy-just-sold.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAF9bNAFfuE/tjiGrny_dvsJkacZuorYzA/view?utm_content=DAF9bNAFfuE&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/the-yellow-letter-strategy-just-sold/example-1-the-yellow-letter-strategy-just-sold.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/the-yellow-letter-strategy-just-sold/example-2-the-yellow-letter-strategy-just-sold.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your