VALUES ('The Yellow Letter Strategy: Truth In Marketing', 'the-yellow-letter-strategy-truth-in-marketing', '<p id="">There''s power when you tell the truth in your marketing.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Bill Bernbach, an American advertising creative director, said ‚ÄúA small admission gains a large acceptance.‚Äù</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This is a principle in advertising.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Tell people what they already know with your direct mail marketing.&nbsp;</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">This strategy is a perfect example.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p>Bonus: We used <a href="https://www.yellowletterscomplete.com/" id="">Yellow Letters Complete</a> to create this campaign. They handwrite the notes using a robot, and you can add a custom sticky note that we find to be extremely effective in eliciting responses.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/the-yellow-letter-strategy-truth-in-marketing/thumbnail-the-yellow-letter-strategy-truth-in-marketing.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAF9bAF1SqQ/dA-SGYTzescuDlcD15XauQ/view?utm_content=DAF9bAF1SqQ&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/the-yellow-letter-strategy-truth-in-marketing/example-1-the-yellow-letter-strategy-truth-in-marketing.png', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/the-yellow-letter-strategy-truth-in-marketing/example-2-the-yellow-letter-strategy-truth-in-marketing.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:</p><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF P