VALUES ('Tre Serrano''s Magic Buyer x Just Sold', 'tre-serranos-magic-buyer-x-just-sold', '<p id="">Here‚Äôs something most agents miss: The best time to market isn‚Äôt after the sale‚Äîit‚Äôs while the momentum is still building.</p><p id="">Recently, my buddy Tre sent me a DM that proves it. He wrote a simple letter for his agent to send out after an Open House. The result? 50 letters. 2 listings.</p><p id="">This approach blends two of the strongest strategies we use at <a target="_blank" href="http://listingleads.com/" id="">ListingLeads.com</a>‚Äîthe Magic Buyer Letter and Storytelling Just Sold. When you combine urgency with a compelling story, people pay attention.</p><p id="">Here‚Äôs the letter. Use it. And more importantly‚Äîstart treating every listing like a launching pad for the next one.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/tre-serranos-magic-buyer-x-just-sold/thumbnail-tre-serranos-magic-buyer-x-just-sold.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGhbU0oWbc/3RyZqIya80MdmItXN4ZJHg/view?utm_content=DAGhbU0oWbc&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', 'https://app.listingleads.com/editor/2b136191-3ea4-4775-bfeb-cab4247b17e2', 'Radius List', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/tre-serranos-magic-buyer-x-just-sold/example-tre-serranos-magic-buyer-x-just-sold.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:<ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selecte