VALUES ('ZMA Letter', 'zma-letter', '<p id="">My friend, Nik Shewmaker send out 80 letters and has already received 2 Come List Me calls. 80 letters. 2 come list me calls. <br><br>Do I need to say more?<br><br>Ok, I will :) </p><p id="">‚Äç<br>This is a campaign known as the ZMA letter. It‚Äôs a simple, but highly effective marketing campaign that helps you start a conversation with prospective sellers.&nbsp;</p><p id="">Now, the 10% doesn‚Äôt matter. It could be 2%, 7.5% or would you sell at this number?</p><p id="">It‚Äôs all designed to create a conversation with the seller.&nbsp;</p><p id="">‚Äç</p><figure id="" class="w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-center" data-rt-type="image" data-rt-align="center"><div id=""><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b3c5fd1ff8bd0fdc5ee861/67bf22ac7f4520dcb4d89843_Screen%20Shot%202025-02-26%20at%209.18.09%20AM.png" loading="lazy" alt="__wf_reserved_inherit" width="auto" height="auto" id=""></div></figure>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/zma-letter/thumbnail-zma-letter.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAGPnhfsGr0/PBb7altVVhb6FGk9vED_lg/view?utm_content=DAGPnhfsGr0&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, 'Farm', 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/zma-letter/example-zma-letter.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:</p><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</strong>: Submit the flattened PDF file to your print shop for printing.</li>"}]', 'US', false, true);

