VALUES ('ZVA', 'zva', '<p id="">This strategy is called Zillow vs Agent.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">(S/O to <a href="https://www.instagram.com/jacobstark_realtor/" id="">Jacob Stark</a> for executing this strategy.)</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">First, a question for you: What happens to the Zestimate when you list a property?</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Right‚Äî<em id="">it changes to the list price.</em></p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Talk about the biggest punch in the gut.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">If you list a property for $500,000 and you sell it for $500,000‚Ä¶it doesn''t appear that you did anything. You simply sold it for the Zestimate.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">What most people <em id="">don''t</em> realize is that maybe two weeks ago, the Zestimate was $430,000.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">But you had no record of proof that you actually sold that property for $70,000 above the Zestimate.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s how to take advantage of that‚Äî</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Before you put the home in the MLS, take a screenshot of the Zestimate.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Then after you sell it, you have a before and after to showcase how great you are at your job.</p><p>‚Äç</p><p id="">Here''s the exact copy to use in your letter.</p>', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/zva/thumbnail-zva.png', 'postcard', 'https://www.canva.com/design/DAF9IlJpE1Y/Z-G9bHttBqVWGLQi6JeoYQ/view?utm_content=DAF9IlJpE1Y&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=publishsharelink&mode=preview', NULL, NULL, 'Direct Mail', NULL, ARRAY['https://ik.imagekit.io/listingleads/Campaigns/Direct%20Mail/zva/example-zva.png'], '[{"title":"Customize Canva Templates to Match Your Brand","body":""},{"title":"Submit to your print shop","body":"<li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Finalize Your Design</strong>: Complete any edits or adjustments in Canva.</li><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Download as PDF</strong>:</p><ul id=\"\"><li id=\"\">Click <strong id=\"\">\"Share\"</strong> in the top right, then select <strong id=\"\">\"Download\"</strong>.</li><li id=\"\">Choose <strong id=\"\">PDF Print</strong> from the file type options.</li><li id=\"\">Ensure the <strong id=\"\">\"Flatten PDF\"</strong> option is selected for compatibility.</li></ul><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Save Your File</strong>: Download the file to your computer.</li><li id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">Send to Print Shop</strong>: Submit the flattened PDF file to your print shop for printing.</li>"}]', 'US', false, true);

